('Hockey World Cup 2024', 2088, 'Shoot on goal and defend against the best in the Hockey World Cup tournament. Are you good enough to win it all and win that trophy?', 'Swipe to shoot mouse or finger Click mouse or tap when defending Keeper will go where you click or tap', 'English'),
