('BFFs Black Friday Collection', 2222, 'Welcome to BFFs Black Friday Collection. Bffs already filled the closet with a new Black Friday outfit. Help them to pick the perfect costume. Don&amp;rsquo;t forget to pick a fabulous hairstyle. They are all excited like us for this day. Join and help the girls with your skill. Play and have fun! Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://cutedressup.com''&gt;https://cutedressup.com&lt;/a&gt;', 'Left Mouse Button Click or tap to play', 'English'),
