('City Bus Parking Challenge Simulator 3D', 2229, 'Welcome to the ultimate test of precision driving skills in the bustling urban environment! City Bus Parking Simulator Challenge 3D offers an immersive and thrilling gaming experience where you take on the role of a skilled bus driver tasked with navigating through complex cityscapes and parking your bus in tight spots.', 'WASD or arrow keys for directions Space for Break', 'English'),
('Math Class', 2230, 'Math Class is a game in which you need to solve various problems with addition, subtraction, division and multiplication. The difficulty will vary depending on the level at which the player is.', 'Use mouse or touch on the screen', 'English'),
('Roly Santa Claus', 2231, 'Dive into the festive fun of Roly Santa Claus, an exciting online game designed for both kids and adults. Your mission: guide Santa on a thrilling adventure, rolling through challenges, collecting delightful gifts, and reaching the safety of the goal. Unleash your gaming spirit and enjoy the joyous journey. Let the rollicking good times begin!', 'A and D or Left and Right arrow to rotate the platform Use left mouse click to cut the rope', 'English'),
