('Alien Jump', 2259, 'Jump around the space with a cute space monster through the galaxy! Collect coins, avoid obstacles and dont fall into the abyss! Get as far as you can! Challenge your friends and find out who is the space king!', 'Press the left side of the screen to move to left Press the right side of the screen to move to right Desktop arrow keyboard keys to move', 'English'),
('Story Teller', 2260, 'Story Teller is a puzzle game full of romance and magic. In front of you is a magical blank storybook to piece together an interactive comic strip, with countless animated sets and personalized characters that will respond to your choices in real time. Use your imagination to complete different types of stories and win the coveted Story Teller crown! Are you ready to explore new worlds?', 'Click or tap to paly', 'English'),
('Cargo Truck: Transport &amp;amp; Hunt', 2261, 'Are you ready for a wild adventure with Cargo Truck: Transport &amp;amp; Hunt, a simulation game that combines driving and hunting? The zoo animals have escaped and you are the only one who can catch them! Drive your truck across the city and use your sniper gun to hunt down the animals, from leopards to elephants. But be careful, they are fast and furious! You have to bring them back to the zoo safely and quickly. Cargo Truck: Transport &amp;amp; Hunt is a game that will challenge your skills and nerves. Don&amp;rsquo;t miss this exciting game! Have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Mien Bugr Skate', 2262, 'Would you like to join the adventurous journey of two cute friends on their skateboards? They need to get home right away. Both friends pink and brown pets have escaped into the streets, so find them and safely return home. Dont forget to collect all the gold coins along the way. Be cautious, as monsters are lurking everywhere, and they might try to devour you.', 'Collect all the badges activate the Black Hole Playable on both desktop and mobile Jump by pressing the W key and the Arrow up key', 'English'),
('Bike Attack Race 2024', 2263, 'Revise your bike and aim at your rivals in thrilling racing battles. While you may have dabbled in various motorcycle racing games, this 3D endless bike race game is a truly challenging, captivating, and utterly addictive experience. It marks a fresh entry into endless drag racing, promising a level of seamless bike racing excitement that is hard to match. This free bike game delivers the most heart-pounding road racing adventure you could ever imagine. Take charge of your bike as you cruise down endless highway roads. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://pl.kizi10.org''&gt;https://pl.kizi10.org&lt;/a&gt;', 'AD left and right drive NM kick left and right W Shotting and use button from the game to fight with other motorcycle', 'English'),
('Kick The Jump', 2264, 'Poke the lazy man to get him from one part of the house to another. While doing all this, be aware of the dangers. Dodge traps, gaps and other items. Make the lazy man reach his goal and make him happy.', 'W A S D or ARROW KEYS', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Wrench &amp;amp; Nuts', 2265, 'In this captivating adventure, multiple wrenches choreograph an intricate dance with numerous screws, demanding both nimble coordination and ingenious sequencing. Assume the role of the maestro of unscrewing, infusing each section with an unmatched flair and surging ahead through a series of heart-pounding challenges. Wrench &amp;amp; bolts is a mind challenging puzzle. Untangle the tangled wrenches in Wrench &amp;amp; bolts puzzle game. Advise smart strategy to solve puzzles of Wrench &amp;amp; bolts. If you enjoy playing knot-solving games like twisted and tangle puzzles Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.laggedgame.com/''&gt;https://www.laggedgame.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'HOW TO PLAY Wrench amp bolts puzzle -Tap on the wrench to unscrew in wrench amp bolts - Retry the level any time you are stuck in wrench amp bolts - Wrench amp bolts is an arcade screw puzzle game - Free the wrenches in order to clear wrench', 'English'),
('Hero Rescue: Pull The Pin', 2266, 'Welcome to Hero Rescue - Pull The Pin puzzle game! Help the hero find the treasures and save the princess right now! You will be a Hero who has the power of wisdom, courage and love to save his bride. The hero started his journey to find the treasure and to save the princess. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://newkidsgames.org''&gt;https://newkidsgames.org&lt;/a&gt;', 'Use mouse or touch on the screen', 'English'),
('Find The Truth Master', 2267, 'Find The Truth Master is a fun puzzle solving game. In this new version of the game, puzzles will be interspersed with episodes that may require you to exercise your brain by breaking the rules and thinking outside the box. If you are a big fan of brain games, then what are you waiting for? Have fun with it!', 'Click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Modern Autumn Outfit', 2268, 'Modern Autumn Outfit is an online game that you can play on Babygames for free. Autumn is coming! Its time to change our wardrobe! So, whats the fashion trend of this season? In this game our fashion girls will show you that, Sofia, Rebecca, Adella will be the models to tell you which clothing you should to pick!', 'Desktop Mouse click and drag to play Mobile Tap and slide to play', 'English'),
('BTC Farmer', 2269, 'BTC Farmer is an instant money idle clicker game that offers a virtual crypto mining experience. Earn money by upgrading to the fastest GPU and speeding up your hardware with new additions. Let your graphics card do the work and increase your speed to make even more money! With a simple interface thats easy to understand, this exciting game provides a virtual crypto mining experience thats perfect for beginners. Start playing online now and enjoy making cash with BTC Farmer !', 'Use the left mouse button to interact with the in-game UI', 'English'),
('Paint Cow', 2270, 'PAINT COW is a captivating game where your task is to paint cows, beginning from the top left corner, to match the color of their adjacent companions.', 'Click or touch to merge cows', 'English'),
('Super Shop Idle Online', 2271, 'Super Shop Idle is a delightful idle game where you can experience the excitement of running your own shop! Put on your entrepreneurial hat and embark on a journey to build the most successful store in town.', 'Desktop Mouse click and drag to play Mobile Tap and slide to play', 'English'),
('Dual Car', 2272, 'DUAL CAR &amp;ndash; Double the Drive, Double the Challenge! Control two cars at the same time! Test your focus and reflexes as you dodge obstacles and collect points on a fast-paced, challenging road. Simple, fun, and addictive &amp;ndash; how long can you last', 'Use the A and B buttons to bypass obstacles', 'English'),
('Manoeuvre FPS', 2273, 'Step into the action with Mini Weapon Simulator, a compact yet thrilling shooting experience designed for quick-fire fun! Progress through bite-sized levels, each crafted to test your aim, timing, and weapon-handling skills. From pistols to powerful rifles, unlock and experiment with a growing arsenal as you advance through each stage. Perfect for fans of shooting games who enjoy focused, level-based challenges without the fluff&amp;mdash;just pure trigger-pulling satisfaction in every round. Start your sharpshooting journey and explore more action-packed browser games at zyrexgames.com &amp;ndash; where every shot hits the mark!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur Reassembled', 2274, 'Step into the delightful chaos of Tung Tung Sahur: Reassembled, a hilarious sliding tile puzzle game where you&amp;rsquo;ll help reassemble the most bizarre and brainrot-worthy characters ever! Your mission? Slide the scrambled tiles to restore wacky portraits of our beloved wooden hero Tung Tung, the elegant yet cursed Ballerina Cappucina, and the determined sneaker-wearing Shark Jogger. Each image is broken into pieces&amp;mdash;can your brain keep up?', 'mouse only', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Blue Koala Jigsaw Puzzles', 2275, 'Get ready to dive into a world of cute and colorful puzzles with Blue Koala Puzzle - Jigsaw Game! This fun and relaxing game is perfect for kids and adults who love jigsaw puzzles and adorable characters. Join Stitch, the mischievous blue koala-like alien from your favorite animated adventures, as he guides you through dozens of beautiful puzzle images!', 'Click and drag pieces to move them', 'English'),
('Bullet Army Run', 2276, 'Welcome to the most exciting army-run challenge! In Bullet Army Run, youll be a commander and lead your Bullet Army on the parkour platforms. This is a casual puzzle game that tests your strategy and reflexes. Collect more bullets and grow your team. Lead the team to avoid obstacles like cutters, hammers, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Kid Cakes Maker Cooking Bakery', 2277, 'Welcome to Kid Cakes Maker Cooking Bakery, a casual cooking simulation game for kids who love food and DIY games. Bake a delicious and beautiful cake with cute animals! Learn to use different cooking tools and master recipes for the best rainbow cake! You need to shop for ingredients and cooking tools in the store. Mix ingredients in the bowl and put the mixture in the moulds to take shape. Heat the cake in the oven.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hair Salon: Beauty Salon', 2278, 'Get ready to unleash your inner hairstylist with the adorable and entertaining game Hair Salon: Beauty Salon! This charming simulation game allows you to run your very own hair salon, where you can give your cute and quirky customers the hair style of their dreams. From washing, styling hair and providing luxurious jewelry &amp;amp; makeup accessories, theres never a dull moment in this delightful game.', 'With a wide range of hairstyles and makeup accessories to choose from you can let your creativity run wild and give your clients a look thats uniquely their own', 'English'),
('Obby Rescue', 2279, 'Obby Rescue is a casual and very funny puzzle game in which the main objective of the game is to protect your adorable little dog from the attack of a swarm of killer bees! The goal of the game is to use the objects that will serve as a barrier against the attack, taking into account at all times your environment and the laws of physics.', 'Use the mouse or touch to play', 'English'),
('Poppy Strike 5', 2280, 'Poppy Strike 5 is a first person shooter game with elements of horror where your mission is to use big arsenal of weapons to shoot huggy wuggy and kisiy misiy and find a way to escape liminal spaces of haunted toy factory.', 'WASD - Move LMB - Shoot RMB - Aim Flashlight R - Reload F - Use G - Grenade H - Melee C - Crouch M - Mute Space - Jump Shift - Run 1-9 - Select Weapon', 'English'),
('My Dress Up Darling', 2281, 'Are you a fashion enthusiast with a passion for all things beautiful? Want to try out new and trendy clothes and makeup? Get ready to enjoy endless creative styles and suits with My Dress Up Darling, the cutest dress-up game online. Designed especially for girl players who love fashion, this casual dress-up game offers a world where you can unleash your inner stylist and create charming looks. We provide plenty of styles, patterns, accessories, and outfits for you.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Labubu Doll Mukbang Asmr Unblocked', 2282, 'Welcome to Labubu Doll Mukbang Asmr Unblocked, a charming, casual ASMR game that combines the joy of food, cooking, and ASMR sounds! Experience as a talented baker and join the lovely Labubu on a mouthwatering adventure. In the game, you will take orders from your diners, each with unique requests for bread. From croissants to loaves of baguettes, you need to pack each bread for your customers on time.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Carrot Climber', 2283, 'Carrot Climber is a cute and fun game where a hungry rabbit climbs walls to collect carrots! Each level has hooks placed on the wall, and you need to help the rabbit jump from one hook to another. Aim carefully&amp;mdash;if you miss, the rabbit will fall! Collect carrots and coins along the way to unlock the next level. It&amp;rsquo;s a sweet mix of challenge and fun for all ages.', 'Desktop Mouse Click Drag to Aim Release to Jump Mobile Touch Drag to Aim Release Finger to Jump', 'English'),
('Celebrity Valentino Pink Collections', 2284, 'Welcome to Celebrity Valentino Pink Collections. Celebrity girls are more famous for their fashion trends. Now they planned to add a new collection to this series. Yes! It&amp;rsquo;s the Valentino Pink collection. They already filled the collection in their wardrobe. Browse and pick a suitable costume for each girl. Join and help the girls in their fashion preparation. Have fun!', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Traffic Trap', 2285, 'Get ready to dive into Traffic Trap, an addictive HTML5 puzzle game perfect for browser play. Control traffic flow on a busy street grid by managing the routes of trucks using directional signs and traffic lights. Each truck follows a marked direction, and one wrong move could lead to a crash! React fast, think smart, and prevent chaos as you unlock new levels with increasing complexity. Use power-ups like hints and bombs to ease tough situations. Ideal for players of all ages, Traffic Trap is optimized for mobile and desktop and is a great choice for monetization through rewarded ads or in-game purchases.', 'Desktop Click on trucks to change direction Mobile Tap trucks to change direction', 'English'),
('Squid Game: Craft Runner', 2286, 'Join the fun in Squid Game Subway Craft! Craft your way through obstacles and race along the railway tracks in a Minecraft-style world. Face exciting challenges, meet cool characters, and show your skills as you survive the ultimate test in this action-packed game inspired by Squid Game! Let me know if this works for you!se!', 'Right Right Arrow or D Left Left Arrow or Q Up Up Arrow or Z Down Down Arrow or S', 'English'),
('Aim', 2287, 'AIM is a term that began to be used during the development of 3d shooters and competitive matches. It was the name of the statistics of hits on target and reaction speed. In this project, you need to use a rebound to set multiple goals at a level. The game features: Advanced object flight physics Good graphics Addictive gameplay Are you ready to upgrade your reaction speed and accuracy? Then start playing! Good luck!', 'When you start the game and select a level you will be greeted by objects on the map there can be from one to ten of them You need to set them in one shot You can fire a shot from anywhere on the level the main thing is to hit all the objects on the', 'English'),
('Anime Doll   DIY Cosplay Girl', 2288, 'Anime Doll - DIY Cosplay Girl is a fashion and lovely dress-up game that presents unprecedented shocking visual effects, providing girls with an amazing dress-up experience! With its stunning graphics and easy-to-use interface, this game is perfect for anyone who loves fashion and adventure.', 'Players simply need to select their preferred clothing items hairstyles and accessories from the games extensive wardrobe selection and apply them to their princess character using the touch and drag controls', 'English'),
('LOL Dolls Nail Salon', 2289, 'Welcome to LOL Dolls Nail Salon, a casual fashion design game for girl players. If you are a doll lover or like doing nail designs, then this game is the perfect place for you. In the game, you are totally on your own to design the fashion nail for your dolls. Dive into the magic fashion nail salon and dazzle the crowd with your charming nail design! You need to start with skin and nail care.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Malatang Master Stack Run 3D', 2290, 'Ready to feel the hottest and most fun parkour game ever? In Malatang Master Stack Run 3D, you become a street food chef. Keep running through colorful 3D platform tracks and collecting tasty ingredients to build the tallest skewer stack ever. Slide to collect noodles, Chicken thighs, chili, and more as you dash forward.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pokemon Memory Time', 2291, 'A Fun Memory Game With Pokemon Magic. Pokemon Memory Time is not just a memory game &amp;mdash; it is a brain-boosting adventure filled with your favorite pocket monsters! Flip colorful cards, uncover hidden Pokemon, and test how well your memory really works. Each round is a playful puzzle that sharpens your mind and warms your heart. Flip Fast and Remember Right!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Night Racing', 2292, 'Get ready for thrilling nighttime races in an adrenaline-filled city! In this game, youll become a true street racer. Jump into the seat of a powerful sports car and hit the streets of the nocturnal city where exciting challenges await you. Complete various missions and perform tricks to showcase your driving skills, evading the police and leaving them far behind. As the game progresses, youll have the opportunity to purchase new, more powerful and faster cars. Become the king of street racing!', 'W - accelerate S - brake reverse A - steer left D - steer right Space - handbrake F - nitro available from the 3rd car M - enlarge map L K - control lights I - start stop the engine C - switch camera Mouse - camera rotation ESC TAB - menu', 'English'),
('Sandbox Squid Game   Create a Challenge', 2293, 'Sandbox Squid Game - Create a Challenge &amp;mdash; a game inspired by Squid Game. The game genre is a sandbox. Therefore, you can freely build whatever you want. The main task is to build a test that players will pass. You can help them, hinder them, or even kill them. When players pass the test, you get money. The game has: more than 5 maps, 4 blocks for construction, more than 5 players, 4 skins for the guard.', 'larr rarr or AD - Right Left uarr or W - Jump Q - Change block S - Place block F - Shoot with machine gun After you build the test dont forget to click on the green button in the upper left corner', 'English'),
('Pixel Slide Puzzle', 2294, 'This is a pixel slide puzzle where you build scenes similar to the classic 15-puzzle &amp;mdash; but with one major twist: every piece can go in any position. Inside, youll find nearly 70 unique levels, each representing a handcrafted pixel illustration. Use the hint feature to preview the completed scene and figure out the correct layout. Perfect for fans of pixel art and relaxing puzzles!', 'Drag and drop pieces to complete the image You can place any piece in any slot Use the hint button to see what the finished level should look like', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('ASMR Games Pretty Princess', 2295, 'Welcome to ASMR Games Pretty Princess, a casual ASMR makeup game for girls. If you are a fan of makeup or dress-up, or love playing princess games, then this is the perfect place for you. Meet various girls and a specific story in the game. Use your wisdom to help the girl get rid of her appearance anxiety. Do skin cleaning, apply cosmetics, add accessories, select beautiful suits...', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Steal Labubu   Sprunki!', 2296, 'Steal Labubu - Sprunki! &amp;ndash; a platformer with physics. You play as Sprunki Pinky. Your task is to carry the found Labubu toy to the green zone. There are 24 levels in the game.', 'Take the toy and bring it to the green field WAD or larr rarr uarr - Movement X or S or darr - Take Throw the toy The game has a double jump', 'English'),
('PFW The Big Shoulder Couture', 2297, 'Welcome to PFW-The Big Shoulder Couture. Celebrity girls are getting ready for another action. Yes! it&amp;rsquo;s Paris Fashion Week! They are excited to try big Shoulder Couture outfits. Browse their wardrobe and pick suitable outfits and accessories. Don&amp;rsquo;t forget to give unique hairstyles. Join them as fashion expert and help the girls to show their stunning fashion looks!', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English'),
('Idol Livestream: Doll Dress Up', 2298, 'In Idol Livestream: Doll Dress Up, you&amp;rsquo;re dressing up your doll and getting her ready to go live. Pick from different styles&amp;mdash;she can look like a fairy, wear chill street clothes, or go for a beach outfit. When you&amp;rsquo;re done, she jumps on the stream and starts showing off her look. You can mess with her hair, add makeup, and try out accessories. There&amp;rsquo;s also a battle mode where you go up against other players to see who styled it best.', 'Dress Up Tap or click to pick outfits and mix styles Go Live Send your doll on stage and watch her perform Battle Enter fashion contests and vote on looks No rush no limits mdash just show off your creativity and style sense', 'English'),
('Stellar Cathcer', 2299, 'Catch the Falling Stars A fast-paced game where you catch falling stars and survive as long as possible. Avoid misses, collect power-ups, and progress through harder levels. Features: Catch stars for points Golden Stars = double points Time Slower slows items Hearts recover misses Bolts boost your speed Shop to unlock skins 5 levels: Easy to Endless Play with keyboard or touch', 'Keyboard Move Left A or larr Move Right D or rarr Touch Mobile Tap left right side of the screen to move', 'English'),
('Skulls And Bombs', 2300, 'Welcome to Skulls And Bombs &amp;mdash; a pirate arcade game where speed means treasure and one mistake leads to an explosion! Click on various items to earn points, but beware of skulls and bombs &amp;mdash; one wrong click and you&amp;rsquo;re sunk! The game gets faster over time, and so do your chances of getting rich&amp;hellip; or not? Test your reflexes and become the fastest pirate on the seas! The golden rule: never click on skulls or bombs. These dangerous objects are thrown in along with the others and can easily trick you. One wrong tap ends the game instantly. So you&amp;rsquo;ll need more than just quick fingers &amp;mdash; you&amp;rsquo;ll need sharp focus. This makes the game not only fast-paced', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Match Memory Online', 2301, 'Looking for an online version of classic Card Matching games? Play a refreshed version of this beloved game here! Win to earn coins and use coins for powerups. Powerups will help you for online matching duels, where you must go against an opponent to match as many cards as possible in one board. As you progress online youll get trophies to advance to new and better leagues, awarding more coins and harder opponents. If youre more of a casual player, you can still play a regular level mode, where you have to find pairs of cards in a bigger and bigger board with a set of lives to do it.You lose a life not finding a pair. Are you ready?Play now', 'Tap a card to reveal Tap 2 cards of same image to get a match Use powerups to win easier', 'English'),
('Sprunky Rich Rich Rich', 2302, 'The Sprunky brothers fall into rivalry and start a competition. Both Sprunky brothers are very ambitious and want to win against each other. In this two-player game, the one who collects and deposits the most money into the piggy bank wins. Collect all the money before your brother and win the game. Be careful &amp;mdash; dangerous objects are coming from everywhere. Dont hit them or youll lose the game!', 'Use WASD keys and Arrow Keys to move bull The first player to collect 50 coins wins the game bull Be careful while collecting money Sharp blades come from the sides and above', 'English'),
('Snakes Eating Blocks', 2303, 'Snake Game is a fun and addictive HTML5 arcade game where you control a green snake using the arrow keys. Eat the red food to grow longer, avoid running into yourself, and try to beat your high score! Designed with responsive controls, smooth animations, and mobile swipe support, this game is perfect for quick and challenging gameplay anytime, anywhere.', 'Use Arrow Keys to move up down right left', 'English'),
('Ellies Recipe: Dubai Chocolate Bar', 2304, 'Whip up luxury in Ellie&amp;rsquo;s Recipe: Dubai Chocolate Bar! Help Ellie create rich, decadent chocolate treats in this fun, interactive cooking game. Gather ingredients, prepare molds, make gourmet fillings, and craft elegant chocolate bars with Dubai flair. Unlock stylish outfits for Ellie and enjoy hands-on cooking fun with real kitchen actions. From mixing to decorating, every step is sweet! Play now and become a luxury dessert pro with Ellie!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Super Meat Boy Online', 2305, 'Super Meat Boy Online is a tough as nails platformer where you play as an animated cube of meat whos trying to save his girlfriend (who happens to be made of bandages) from an evil fetus in a jar wearing a tux. Our meaty hero will leap from walls, over seas of buzz saws, through crumbling caves and pools of old needles.', 'Use the mouse or touch to play', 'English'),
('Mahjong Master Challenge', 2306, 'Ready to flip tiles, race the clock and sharpen your mind? MahjongMasterChallenge packs many handcrafted mahjong layouts into one fun puzzle journey. Your goal: clear the board by matching identical or coherent tiles. For example, chow: Combine two pairs into a sequence to clear. Kong: Combine two pairs into four of a kind to clear. Use your logic skills to eliminate and keep upgrading.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('TickTock Challenge', 2307, 'Looking for the craziest brain teaser ever? Welcome to TickTock Challenge! This is a superb collection of minigames! From fun bubble shooter action to relaxing 2048 puzzles, from clever match and merge challenges to salon-themed brain teasers. This game has it all! Every level brings a new surprise, pushing you to think faster and smarter under the pressure of the ticking clock! Each round is quick, crazy, and incredibly fun.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('My Baby Unicorn Pony Care 2', 2308, 'Welcome to My Baby Unicorn - Pony Care, a casual baby pet care game for girl players. You will witness the birth of the baby unicorn, take care of him, and play with him! If you are a pet lover, do not miss this pet care simulation game. Have endless fun seeing the little unicorn growing up! Click on the different icons to feed the baby with food, soothe him to sleep, and try perfect dress-up. Earn extra stars and energies after you finish each care task.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Death Worm 2', 2309, 'The Death Worm has surfaced. In Death Worm, you control a colossal underground monster, bursting through the earth to wreak havoc in a thrilling mix of arcade, action, and casual destruction. There are different modes for you to choose from. For example, enter level mode. Swimming underground at high speeds, locking onto prey and breaking through the ground to complete the fatal attack. Eliminate humans, helicopters, cars, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('SnakeGamePro', 2310, 'elive the retro arcade thrill with a modern twist! Classic Snake Pro brings back the iconic arcade experience with sleek visuals, smooth controls, and addictive gameplay. Navigate your snake to munch on glowing food, grow longer, and avoid collisions with walls&amp;mdash;or yourself! Features: Modern Retro Design &amp;ndash; Vibrant colors, smooth animations, and a clean grid layout. Intuitive Controls &amp;ndash; Play with keyboard (arrow keys) or touchscreen (swipe gestures). Speed Boost &amp;ndash; Game gets faster as you score, testing your reflexes! High Score System &amp;ndash; Compete against yourself and unlock new records. Pause &amp;amp; Resume &amp;ndash; Take a break anytime and ju', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('ASMR Girl: Livestream Mukbang', 2311, 'Step into the world of ASMR Girl: Livestream Mukbang, where you take on the role of an adorable mukbang streamer! Get ready to indulge in delicious food, satisfy your cravings, and share the experience with your viewers in a cozy, interactive livestream. The more you eat and engage, the more you earn!', 'Shop Cook and Enjoy Delicious Foods Live Stream Your Mukbang Adventures Earn Money Upgrade Your Girl and Buy More Food', 'English'),
('Gem Dojo', 2312, 'Gem Dojo Match gems. Master skills. Become the ultimate puzzle ninja. Welcome to Gem Dojo, where stealth meets strategy in a vibrant match-3 puzzle adventure set in the world of ninjas! Train in the ancient art of gem-matching to unleash powerful combos, defeat rival ninjas, and rise through the ranks of the secret dojo. Swap and match colorful gems to charge up your ninja abilities, unlock hidden techniques, and outsmart increasingly tricky puzzle challenges. Only the sharpest minds and fastest fingers can become true masters of the Gem Dojo.', 'Match-3 and win bonuses', 'English'),
('Fun Mini Games For Princess', 2313, 'Welcome to Fun Mini Games For Princess, a collection of mini casual games for kids. Dive into the gaming world and enjoy the fun of playing at your fingertips! Whether you are a casual gamer who looks for relaxation or a skillful player with a purpose, you will find your favorite game and enjoy endless fun in our mini games. Our mini games cover a large range of categories.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Animal Racing 2', 2314, 'Face the wildest race of your life in Animal Racing. It&amp;rsquo;s a full-blown arcade adventure filled with running, transforming, and brain-tickling puzzles! Youll be running on platforms with your opponents. Outsmart your opponents in epic simulator-style racing challenges. Quick response to transform into different animals on different platforms. For example, transforming a shark to cross the sea, an eagle to fly over a gap, an orangutan to run up a flight of steps.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Skibidi Toilet Melon Sandbox', 2315, 'Welcome to Skibidi Toilet Melon Sandbox, where youll embark on a journey in epic battlefield with brave warrior. These Casual Merge Games bring exquisite model and scene, immersing battle master in the strategic challenges between monsters and warriors. In Monster Battle toilet games, take on the role of a strategic Battle Master, defeating toilet warriors by synthesizing fight monster! Toilet games emphasize thinking, make key decisions that affect victory or defeat!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Squishmallow Coloring Book', 2316, 'Get ready to color your favorite Squishmallow! Weve got over 16 adorable Squishmallow pictures just waiting for your creative touch.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Animal cards memory', 2317, 'Animal Cards Memory is a game that helps you train your memory. No matter how old you are, these types of games are useful at any age. The game consists of 7 levels that become more difficult as you go ahead. Animal memory card games are more than just a source of entertainment; they are a dynamic educational resource that adapts to modern lifestyles. By combining accessibility, variety, and interactive learning, these games not only engage children but also lay the groundwork for essential cognitive and social skills that will benefit them in the long run.', 'Mouse for the computer devices and finger for touch devices', 'English'),
('Crazy Bouncer', 2318, 'Bounce your way to victory! Take control of a bouncy ball in this fun and challenging platformer. Jump, roll, and dodge through tricky obstacles, deadly traps, and moving platforms as you aim to reach the green flag at the end of each level. Master the timing of your jumps by charging and releasing to gain extra height. Precision and patience are the key&amp;mdash;can you make it through all levels without falling? With colorful graphics, satisfying controls, and physics-based gameplay, this game is perfect for fans of casual and skill-based games. Reach the green flag, avoid the red zones, and prove your bouncing skills!', 'Controls Arrow Keys or A D ndash Move Left Right Spacebar ndash Hold to charge jump release to jump Touch Controls Mobile Tap left side to move Tap and hold right side to charge jump release to jump Timing and precision are key Hold your jump', 'English'),
('Screw Sort Puzzle Pin Jam 3D', 2319, 'Want a fun 3D puzzle that&amp;rsquo;s strangely relaxing? In ScrewSortPuzzle:PinJam3D, you&amp;rsquo;ll remove every screw, sort colorful pins, and match them to the right slots without causing a jam! You will have to keep matching the screws of the right color and put them in the box of the corresponding color. Rotate the board to spot the screws you can safely loosen first. You can experience remove screw mode.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Moe Kittens Cat Avatar Maker', 2320, 'Have you got the idea of raising a pet? Do you like playing with lovely cats? Welcome to Moe Kittens: Cat Avatar Maker, a cat avatar simulator game online. You can create your own kitten in every detail, from colors, shapes, tails, to patterns. Various colors and patterns for you to choose from. Never stop creating new fashion! Easy control allows players of all skill levels to enjoy.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Candy Monster Raffi', 2321, 'Help the candy monster Raffi eat all the candies! He absolutely loves them &amp;ndash; all he wants is to eat candy. But be careful while collecting them! If you jump in the wrong direction, you might hit dangerous spikes. This cute little monster is hungry &amp;ndash; run and feed Raffi with as many candies as you can!', 'Click on the candy just in time to eat the candies watch out for obstacles collect coins buy other costumes The game is available to play on both mobile devices and desktop computers', 'English'),
('Mickey Run Adventure Game', 2322, 'Welcome to the great kingdom craft! prepare yourself brave mickey, get ready to run, jump, dash and rush through the kingdom. In this craft game, you will be a runner who has to run and collect coins in an endless runner game mine. You need to be very careful as there will be many mouse in your way. You will need to use your craft Mickey and reflexes to avoid them and keep running. There will also be power-ups that you can collect to help you in the craft game.', 'Up Arrow - Jump Left Arrow - Move Left Right Arrow - Move Right Down Arrow - Slide', 'English'),
('Stupid Arrow', 2323, 'Blunt Arrow is a one&amp;ndash;of-a-kind action game that can train your reflexes to perfection. Try to walk to the end of the rapidly narrowing circle. The arrow cannot penetrate several objects, you will have to make a lot of accurate shots, and then reach the end. The game offers: Unique gameplay Good graphics Development of reaction and precision Hurry up and start playing, beat your friends high score and collect the rewards!', 'You start the game in the center of the circle your task is to get out of the circle by shooting accurately at the platforms the circle is constantly narrowing Can you get out of it', 'English'),
('HoppyRushy', 2324, 'The character moves back and forth on the platform, controlling the characters upward jump to the safe platform. Coins are awarded during the game, and coins can unlock other characters. Lets see how many platforms you can skip.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Bubble Pop Frenzy', 2325, 'Bubble Pop Frenzy is a fast-paced arcade game where you pop bubbles to score points while avoiding dangerous bomble traps. The game speeds up the longer you play, testing your reflexes and focus. With retro-inspired visuals, smooth controls, and a catchy synthwave soundtrack, its easy to pick up and hard to put down. Try to beat your high score and survive the frenzy!', 'Click or tap on bubbles to pop them Avoid clicking on the bomble That rsquo s all you need to know mdash fast reactions are key', 'English'),
('Labubu Zombie Miner', 2326, 'Labubu got lost in the mine while searching for gold and valuable minerals. The mines owner, a zombie miner, is chasing Labubu. Labubu must escape safely. Help him escape and reach the parchment at the end of the mine. The parchment is very important &amp;mdash; it contains the way out of the mine. Reach the parchment safely!', 'Press W the key to jump Playable on both mobile and PC Double jump available', 'English'),
('Fruit Merge: Juicy Drop Game', 2327, 'Dive deep into the vibrant and enthralling world of fruit-matching with our exciting game, Fruit Merge: Juicy Drop Game! When the same fruits collide, they merge into a larger fruit. Your mission is to smartly pair the same types of fruits to make the biggest possible fruits without letting them overflow from the container. However, as the fruits grow in size, space becomes a premium - managing it effectively is your key challenge. Can you strategize and solve this fruity puzzle?', 'Challenge yourself and create a giant fruit Start by merging two smaller fruits to eventually form a gigantic one It rsquo s a feat only 1 of players have achieved Are you ready to join that elite group', 'English'),
('Roblox In Barbie Style', 2328, 'Barbie meets the world of Roblox in this fun fashion game that lets you mix high-style outfits with blocky avatars. In Roblox in Barbie Style, your job is to style your Roblox character in pinks, sparkles, heels, and iconic Barbie-inspired outfits that pop.', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'English'),
('Martial Artist', 2329, 'This time, you are a martial artist, and you will experience the combination of killing and strategy. See how far you can last! Simple click controls and pixel graphics make this game perfect for casual players!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Run Guys: Knockout Royale', 2330, 'Enjoy chaos, laughter, and action in Run Guys: Knockout Royale. A running and multiplayer royale game. In seesaw mode, run over one seesaw after another, keep balance and rush to the finish line. Racing at breakneck speeds through spinning wooden columns, trap floors and trap obstacles. Each level will knock out the slowest players. In mountain climbing, be the first to reach the summit and jump onto the crown.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Construction Simulator', 2331, 'Ready to build big and drive even bigger. Construction Simulator brings you into the most realistic world of construction driving simulation. Designed for boys who love mechanics, speed and challenges.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ballerina Cappuccina First Date', 2332, 'Tonight&amp;rsquo;s a big night&amp;mdash;Cappuccina and Tung Tung Sahur are heading out on their very first date, and they want to look perfect. In Ballerina Cappuccina First Date, you&amp;rsquo;re the stylist behind their special evening. From choosing outfits to adding finishing touches, it&amp;rsquo;s up to you to make sure both of them shine.', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'English'),
('HexaPuzzleNew', 2333, 'Drag the blocks and place them in the container above to assemble them. Its very fun and has multiple exquisite levels. Come and experience it now.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Snake 2025', 2334, 'Snake 2025 is a modern remake of the classic snake game with sleek graphics and smooth controls. Navigate the snake to collect orbs, grow longer, and compete for high scores. Featuring updated mechanics, retro-inspired visuals, and fast-paced arcade action. A perfect mix of nostalgia and challenge!', 'Arrow Keys or WASD to move Avoid hitting yourself or the walls', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Pixel Draw', 2335, 'Unleash your creativity by crafting unique pixel art from scratch. In Pixel Draw, there are no templates &amp;mdash; only your imagination and a grid waiting to be filled. Whether youre sketching a hero, a symbol, or something abstract, this is your chance to become a true pixel artist. Save your masterpiece and share it with friends to showcase your talent.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('The Ink Shop Tattoo Art ASMR', 2336, 'Step into the evocative world of tattoo artistry with The Ink Shop - Tattoo Art ASMR. Designed to offer a unique blend of creativity and relaxation, the application puts you in the role of a skilled tattoo artist, responsible for turning clients visions into stunning inked realities. This immersive game not only allows you to explore artistic expressions but also provides the soothing ambiance of ASMR through every phase of the tattooing process.', 'At the heart of the app you will encounter customers each with a unique backstory and tattoo ideas Your task is to guide them through the tattoo journey - from preparing the skin with shaves and antiseptics to the meticulous inking With hundreds of des', 'English'),
('Tung TungBall and Labububall', 2337, 'You must survive in the world of balls. Two friends, Tungball and Labububall, need your help. They must collect all the coins, escape from the forest, find the key, and unlock the castle gate. Both friends must reach the castle safely. Reach the castle safely and earn the right to move on to the next level. Be careful &amp;mdash; if the shelled monsters catch you, you&amp;rsquo;ll lose.', 'Move to WASD Arrow Keys Double Jump available Mobile Touch Control Collect all the coins and the golden key then reach the gate', 'English'),
('Amazing Paper Doll Diary', 2338, 'Welcome to Amazing Paper Doll Diary, a collection of casual mini-games, exclusively for girl players. If you are searching for relaxation online, do not hesitate to join our amazing game selection! Whether you prefer fashion design, doll dress-up, or animal games, you can enjoy a relaxing and refreshing gaming experience with our mini-games. Play the paper doll game in an easy and reactive way.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Geometry Jump Dash', 2339, 'Jump, dash, and fly through a pulse-pounding obstacle course where one wrong move means disaster! This fast-paced, high-energy arcade game challenges players of all skill levels with precision platforming, rhythmic obstacles, and adrenaline-fueled gameplay.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Anime Couple: Avatar Maker', 2340, 'Anime Couple: Avatar Maker, the ultimate anime avatar character creation experience! Dive into the world of anime with our cutting-edge app that lets you design anime avatar faces, dress up girl avatars, and create the coolest anime couple characters youve ever seen.', 'Whether youre into cute and sweet anime couples or edgy and mysterious ones Anime Couple Avatar Maker has you covered With our comprehensive selection of features and customization options youll never run out of possibilities', 'English'),
('Volleyball Fun Coloring', 2341, 'Dive into the colorful world of Volleyball Fun Coloring: a cheerful and free online coloring game where kids can spike their creativity and serve up bright beach vibes one crayon at a time!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Zoo Anomaly Simulation', 2342, 'Experience a zoo mutation crisis like no other. In Zoo Anomaly Simulation, a peaceful zoo has turned into a nightmare filled with mutated animals, and you&amp;rsquo;re the only one who can stop the chaos! Enter a first-person shooting experience like no other. Explore the eerie zoo environment, grab your weapons, and fight back against giraffes, zebras, elephants, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Swing Hero', 2343, 'Swing Hero is an action-packed adventure game where a monkey swings down a cliff using a rope! As the monkey slides down, obstacles like rocks and snakes block the way. You need to swing left and right to avoid hitting them. It&amp;rsquo;s a thrilling and fun game that tests your timing and reflexes. How far can your monkey swing?', 'Desktop Mouse Drag Swing Rope Mobile Click and hold Swing Rope', 'English'),
('Where is my Water', 2344, 'Help Swampy by guiding water to his broken shower. Each level is a challenging physics-based puzzle with amazing life-like mechanics. Cut through dirt to guide fresh water, dirty water, toxic water, steam, and ooze through increasingly challenging scenarios! Every drop counts!', 'Use the mouse or touch to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Dinosaur Shifting Run', 2345, 'Imagine sprinting across a scorching desert as a human adventurer, then transforming into a mighty dinosaur to smash through obstacles in a lush jungle! Unlike other runner games, Dinosaur Shifting Run offers unique challenges in every level, keeping the gameplay fresh and exciting.', '- Transform the character to suit the environment - Make sure you choose the right one to become the winner - The higher level it is the more difficult game-play it is', 'English'),
('Super Robot Chogokin', 2346, 'Play a relaxing destruction game in Super Robot Chogok. You control a giant robot. Smash, crash, and destroy everything in your path. This game is perfect for any boy who dreams of robot domination! The gameplay is super simple and satisfying. Guide your robot through the city, crash into cars, buildings, etc. Unleash powerful moves to destroy and avoid damage!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Great ZigZag Game 3D', 2347, 'Hello! Change the direction of the ball by clicking on the screen and try not to fall! You earn points with each click! Try to get the highest score! Be careful, if you accidentally fall, you lose! Be the one who gets the highest score among your friends! Are you ready to have fun with this zigzag game played with simple logic? If you are ready, why are you waiting! Start playing this zigzag game suitable for all ages right away! Be careful, the game will get faster and harder! But we have no doubt that you will get the highest score thanks to your skills!', 'When you click on the screen the direction of the ball changes', 'English'),
('Cinema Empire Idle Tycoon', 2348, 'Welcome to Cinema Empire Idle Tycoon! Do you dream of owning your own movie theater empire? Nows your chance! In this super fun idle simulation management game, youll start with a small screening room! Build your own cinema empire! As a theater owner, you need to manage every aspect of the theater. Unlock the theaters facilities, ticket booths, movie halls, dining areas, and more. Hiring employees to help you get more bang for your buck.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Geometry Rash', 2349, 'Geometry Rash is a high-speed action platformer where every move counts. Jump your way through 8 challenging levels filled with spikes and traps. As you progress, you&amp;rsquo;ll unlock new gameplay forms, fly with the ship or boost with the rocket. Mastering each style is key to surviving later levels. Along the way, collect coins to unlock fresh character looks in the shop. With tight controls and tough level design, this game will test your reflexes and rhythm!', 'Tap or click to jump You begin with the cube form As you beat levels you rsquo ll unlock the ship and rocket forms each with different movement In rocket form hold to fly upward and release to fall Time your moves to dodge traps and collect coins', 'English'),
('Fish master', 2350, 'Master of Fishing - a new project for fans to sit with a fishing rod, and just relax. The game will give you extremely positive emotions, here you will be able to catch the fish you want, but you have to try. The game offers: - Meditative gameplay - Nice drawn graphics - Realistic fishing Are you ready to cast your rod and pull in your biggest catch? Then go for it!', 'Your character is in a boat and all you have to do is fish Cast your line and fish gradually upgrade your equipment and pull in more and more fish good luck', 'English'),
('Bitcoin.io', 2351, '&amp;lt;Chomp your way to the top in Bitcoin.io &amp;ndash; the crypto-themed multiplayer madness! Munch coins and energy to grow bigger, dodge rivals, and dominate the leaderboard in this fast-paced online arena. It is free, frantic, and super fun. Are you ready to become the biggest Bitcoin in the blockchain?', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('The Long Drive', 2352, 'Love driving games? Love car simulation but keen on racing? Then you definitely cant miss The Long Drive! This is a real and crazy driving simulation game for boys who love adventure! In this open world, you drive a car and start your challenge. In Free Mode, you can complete various challenges and earn rewards.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Physical Ball', 2353, 'Physics Balls is Suit for all age and completely FREE to play! Now become the master of the Physic Balls! Features: Perfect physic ball bouncy engine Fully automatic progress save Endless game mode Tablet support', 'Aim at breaking all bricks by one shoot Swipe your finger and throw balls Make them roll among the bricks Hit items to make extra balls or double size ball Prevent the bricks to reach the check-line', 'English'),
('Unblocked Forest Fireboy And Watergirl', 2354, 'Want a mind-bending and action forest adventure in Unblocked Forest Fireboy And Watergirl? Play alone or with friends and join adventures! This classic multiplayer puzzle game brings the iconic Fireboy and Watergirl duo back into a mysterious Forest temple. Silent cooperation is the only way to get through! Each collects gems and gold coins of the corresponding color. Push the boxes, press the switches, and cooperate with each other to pass the level successfully.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('ROAD CROSSER', 2355, 'This is a 3D casual game. You can control the character to eat coins while avoiding cars. Coins can be used to buy new and cuter skins.', 'Keyborard', 'English'),
('Quick Shot', 2356, 'Quick Shot is a fast-paced online shooting game where precision is everything. Your goal is simple: hit each target exactly in the center to score the highest points. But be careful &amp;mdash; you can only miss five times before the game ends. With quick reflexes and sharp aim, you&amp;rsquo;ll need to stay focused as the targets appear faster and more unpredictably. How long can you keep your streak alive? Test your skills and aim for perfection in Quick Shot!', 'Tap on the game screen to play this game', 'English'),
('Online Cats Multiplayer Park', 2357, 'Come to run, jump, guess, and race as a cute but competitive kitty in Online Cats - Multiplayer Park. It&amp;rsquo;s a real-time multiplayer chaos arena. Here are seven modes you can choose from. In Grab A Shabby Ball, for example, you will have to compete with your opponents and try to touch the ball to get points.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Fruit Memory Extravaganza', 2358, 'Fruit Memory Extravaganza is a vibrant and juicy card-based memory game that challenges your brain and sharpens your recall skills! Flip cards one by one to find matching fruit pairs &amp;mdash; from bananas to berries &amp;mdash; all within a limited time. With 6 increasingly tricky levels, each round gets faster and more challenging, testing how quickly and accurately you can match the fruity duos. Can you conquer the fruit frenzy before the clock runs out? Key Features: Flip-and-match fruit cards in a race against time Boosts memory and concentration skills Time-limited challenges across all levels Colorful fruit-themed visuals', 'Match the cards click to flip', 'English'),
('Fide The Hole', 2359, 'Continuation of the successful game Physical Maze, updated graphics and sounds have been added in the new part. The number of levels has also almost doubled! Now you need to complete the levels, avoiding obstacles. The levels have become more difficult, and the physical model will delight sophisticated players with its sophistication. Start playing, get rewards and unlock new levels! Develop spatial thinking!', 'To play you will need a mouse or the screen of your smartphone Start completing the first level and discover a new physics model The game is made with an emphasis on developing your spatial thinking Therefore its not just entertainment its also a gr', 'English'),
('Tap Cute Animals', 2360, 'Get ready to unwind in a cheerful clicker adventure where every tap brings rewards. In Tap Cute Animals, you&amp;rsquo;ll collect coins, unlock adorable creatures, and dress them up in all sorts of quirky hats. Combine animals and outfits to craft delightful styles, explore charming new worlds, and upgrade your clicking power to progress faster. Its a fun and cozy way to spend your time!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Mahjong Fruit 3D', 2361, 'Before you on the screen will be seen a three-dimensional image of cubes on the faces of which you will see various images of fruits. You will need to carefully examine everything, find the same fruits completely and clicking on them to highlight the cubes on which they are applied. Having done this, you will see how these objects will disappear from the game field. For this, you will accrue points and you will make the next move. Your task in the game Mahjong Fruit 3D in the minimum time and the number of moves completely clean the field of cubes.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Musical Labubu: Make a Melody', 2362, 'Musical Labubu - Make a Melody is a game about creating your own melody in a small 3D world. Here youll see a variety of Labubu, with a variety of animations and sounds. The game features a night mode that can really surprise and scare you. If youre not afraid, youll love it. Come on in and create your favorite melody!', 'Drag the Labubu icons from the bottom of the screen onto the stage Each Labubu plays its own melody so create a variety of melodies and enjoy the game', 'English'),
('Pass the ball 3d', 2363, 'The ball must be kicked so that it bounces off various objects and flies exactly into the green container. Watch the behavior of the defenders, they can easily hit the ball.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('LOL Presidential Face', 2364, 'LOL Presidential Face is a funny and lighthearted face-editing game where you can mix, stretch, and swap presidential features in hilarious ways. Pick from different presidents, drag and distort their faces, add goofy accessories, and create the funniest combinations you can imagine. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re making them look silly, serious, or just plain ridiculous, the goal is simple: laugh out loud at your presidential masterpiece and share it with friends.', 'mouse only', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Bus Route', 2365, 'The BUS ROUTE is a colourful and fun puzzlesorting game created by gameNply.com In this game: You have a queue of passengers waiting for their bus, each passenger having different colours, Your task is to sort them by colour, match them up in the right way, and organize the flow so that VIP passengers or special ones can board on time, The game features smooth animations, lively backgrounds, and vibrant, bus-themed visuals. As you progress, it gets more challenging: more colours, more passengers, more pressure to sort quickly and efficiently, It&amp;rsquo;s simple to get into but clever in design&amp;mdash; Thanks for Play', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Arrows disappear', 2366, 'Tap on the blocks to make them fly off the screen. Remove all the blocks to complete the level. Try to handle large amounts of blocks when you have a limit on the number of moves and every mistake will bring you closer to failure.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Obby: Training by Car', 2367, 'Get ready to drive as far as possible, buy new cars, unlock new trails, and collect energy! Buy awesome cars, and collect energy and pets that give you powerful bonuses! Explore different locations. Game Features: &amp;bull; Control your car. &amp;bull; Farm energy to make your car faster. &amp;bull; Unlock unique trails with special effects. &amp;bull; Revive system &amp;ndash; unlock new locations and grow stronger. &amp;bull; Leaderboards &amp;amp; competitions &amp;ndash; race against other players and become the champion! Can you become the best racer?', 'bull Movement ndash W A S D bull Jump ndash Spacebar', 'English'),
('Tracky Tracks', 2368, 'Tracky Tracks (Tricky Tracks) &amp;mdash; fast-paced drifting game of precision and speed! Race through mountains, cities, and lakes, customize your car, and master challenging tracks with smooth, responsive controls.', 'W S FORWARD BACKWARD A D RIGHT LEFT SPACE BRAKE ESC GO TO MAIN MENU P PAUSE R RESTART C CHANGE CAMERA', 'English'),
('Bus Simulator Unblocked Remastered', 2369, 'Bus Simulator Unblocked Remastered lets you drive legit routes in your browser&amp;mdash;no installs, no drama. Climb into a first-person cockpit, start the engine, signal, open doors, and keep to the schedule while traffic AI and tight corners test your patience. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesx.com/.''&gt;https://www.crazygamesx.com/.&lt;/a&gt; Smooth WebGL visuals, decent physics, and multiple camera views make runs feel real. Perfect for school Chromebooks or quick breaks. WASD to drive, Q/E for indicators, space to brake&amp;mdash;don&amp;rsquo;t miss those stops.', 'Mouse click or tap to play WASD to drive the bus', 'English'),
('Brainrot Click to Hatch', 2370, 'Enter Brainrot Click to Hatch, the absurd and epic clicker where every tap hatches chaotic BRAINROTS. Unlock characters like Bombardero Cocodrilo, Tralalero Tralala, Lirali Liralira, and Chimpancini Bananini, then push them to their MAX POWER forms with epic transformations. Earn coins, unlock upgrades, and speed your progress. Discover special day/night backgrounds and watch your collection grow stranger and more powerful. From viral classics to impossible evolutions, the challenge is clear: collect them all before losing your mind!', 'Use the left mouse button to play and interact with the in-game UI', 'English'),
('Quick Cards', 2371, 'Keep throwing the cards on your turn, the larger card wins! The winner keeps both the cards. In case of tie, the game is on! The more you play, the more you like the game.', 'Keep throwing cards', 'English'),
('Noob vs Pro But Knife Hit Minecraft', 2372, 'A two-player game where the luckiest and most calculating wins! Noob and Pro decided to play a so-called darts game, but with knives. A fun two-player game in the style of Minecraft and Knife Hit. The game features: -Two-player mode -Single-player mode -20+ level variations -20+ single-player level variations -10 bosses -Sharp knives -Logs (just logs) -Workbenches (both spinning and non-spinning, but thats a matter of taste) -Fragile sand blocks -Evil bosses -Strange levels -And much more! The main goal of the game is to throw knives at logs until they run out.', 'Controls on PC 1 player Pro Z key - shoot knife 2 player Noob Up arrow - shoot knife In two-player mode shoot knives in turns In single-player mode shoot by pressing the up arrow Controls on Mobile Tap the screen to shoot a knife', 'English'),
('Noob vs Pro But Floor is Lava Minecraft', 2373, 'Noob and Pro decided to relax, but suddenly rising lava ruined their plans! Now they&amp;rsquo;re trying to survive in this lava-filled world! A fun two-player game in a Minecraft style. The game features: -Two-player mode -Single-player mode -12 main levels plus 2 special levels -Hot lava -Jump and speed potions found in chests -Falling sand blocks -Levels with lava lakes -And much more! The main goal is to avoid falling into the lava, which rises higher and higher each round. Occasionally, the lava will lower to give you a brief break. 1 Player mode also available!', 'On PC Pro controls A D to move left and right W to jump Noob controls Left arrow Right arrow to move Up arrow to jump On Mobile Pro controls joystick Noob controls joystick', 'English'),
('Super Girls My Rainy Day Outfits', 2374, 'Welcome to Super Girls My Rainy Day Outfits. Who said that you can&amp;rsquo;t look perfect on a rainy day? A bit of rain shouldn&amp;rsquo;t stop us from looking fabulous! And don&amp;rsquo;t even worry about the hair, some curls under a hat look absolutely perfect! How would your perfect rainy day outfit look like? Try creating it while helping these princesses dress up in warmer clothes and rain boots. Accessorize their look with a hat, scarf, and a cute umbrella.', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Om Nom Run 03', 2375, 'Om Nom Run is an exciting endless runner where you guide Om Nom through fun and colorful levels, jumping over obstacles and collecting tasty candies. The goal is simple: run as far as you can, score points, and beat your high score! With easy one-button controls, anyone can pick up and play, making it perfect for kids and adults alike. The further you run, the faster the game becomes, testing your reflexes and timing. Avoid dangerous obstacles, grab candies for bonus points, and try to survive as long as possible. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re looking for a quick game to pass the time or a real challenge to push your limits, Om Nom Run delivers fast-paced', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Road Fighter &amp;ndash; Endless Car Racing', 2376, 'Hit the road in Road Fighter, a fast-paced 3-lane racing game! Dodge traffic, avoid oil spills, and race against time while climbing the leaderboard. Collect points to level up and increase your speed. Can you survive the traffic and become the ultimate road champion? Features: 3 lanes with smooth left/right movement Obstacles: cars and oil spills Increasing speed and levels for extra challenge Real-time scoring and leaderboard support Mobile-friendly with touch controls Sound effects and background music for immersive gameplay', 'Desktop Arrow Left A Move left Arrow Right D Move right Arrow Up W Accelerate Arrow Down S Brake Mobile Touch Left button Move left Right button Move right Accelerate button Increase speed Brake button Slow down', 'English'),
('Black And White 2', 2377, 'Black and White 2 is a fast-paced arcade game where you control a cube that switches between black and white. Jump over obstacles, adapt to shifting patterns, and survive as long as you can. Each zone you clear restores your 6 lives, but when they run out it&amp;rsquo;s game over. The Game Over screen shows how far you made it before giving you the chance to retry and jump straight back into the action. With its minimalist design, sharp contrast, and addictive gameplay, Black and White delivers a modern arcade experience that&amp;rsquo;s easy to pick up but hard to master.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Noob vs Pro But Anvil Rain Minecraft', 2378, 'Noob and Pro decided to sit down and relax, but a sudden anvil rain ruined their plans! Now they&amp;rsquo;re trying to survive in this world! A fun two-player game in the style of Minecraft. The game features: Two-player mode Single-player mode 12 main levels 3 single-player levels Hot lava Heavy and noisy anvils Falling sand blocks (its a tradition by now) Levels with lava lakes Strange levels? And much more! The main goal is to dodge the falling anvils. The longer you survive, the more anvils will fall every second!', 'On PC Pro controls A D to move left and right W to jump Noob controls Left arrow Right arrow to move Up arrow to jump On Mobile Pro controls joystick Noob controls joystick', 'English'),
('People tower', 2379, 'We need to get to the finish line, but there are many obstacles ahead that will have to be bypassed. Collect people along the way to form a high pyramid, so you will definitely go all the way.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Super Basketball Bluey', 2380, 'Super Basketball is a simple yet incredibly addictive game built on realistic physics! Just tap and slide the ball to adjust the angle and power, then shoot it straight into the hoop. With smooth physics and visual effects, every shot looks clear and exciting. It&amp;rsquo;s an endless arcade challenge: score to advance through levels as the difficulty rises with four different random hoop movements. But be careful &amp;mdash; you only have 3 shots to complete each level! HOW TO PLAY: Tap the screen. Drag the ball to adjust power and angle. Release to shoot!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Whats In My Bag?', 2381, 'Unpack style and surprises in What&amp;rsquo;s In My Bag? &amp;ndash; the ultimate dress-up and makeup game for fashion lovers! Choose cute outfits, glam makeup, and trendy bags, then reveal what&amp;rsquo;s inside each one. From influencer props to girly goodies, every bag tells a story. Get creative, show off your style, and join the viral &amp;ldquo;what&amp;rsquo;s in my bag&amp;rdquo; trend now! Perfect for fans of dress-up games, makeup fun, and aesthetic vibes.', 'Use your mouse to play the game on a desktop tap to play on mobile devices', 'English'),
('Slither Mini Kingdom', 2382, 'Control a glowing snake in a competitive arena, eating dots to grow longer while outmaneuvering other players. Avoid colliding with your rivals to survive, and trap them to turn them into food. Your goal is simple: become the longest snake and dominate the leaderboard.', 'Mouse to control amp space button to boost in phone use joystick to move', 'English'),
('Happy Gunman', 2383, 'Your salvation is in your hands, in order to survive, you need to take accurate shots at your pursuers. All forces are thrown in pursuit of you, even using dinosaurs to chase you.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Obby: Climb and Slide', 2384, 'Ready to conquer the tallest slides? In this game, you can! Climb higher and higher up the ladders, then rush down the thrilling slides! The farther you slide, the more coins you collect! And with cute pets by your side, you&amp;rsquo;ll earn even more &amp;mdash; they&amp;rsquo;ll help you gather coins! What awaits you: &amp;bull; Long ladders and exciting slides for speedy rides &amp;bull; Funny pet companions &amp;bull; Bright levels and new heights &amp;bull; Fun gameplay and colorful graphics Climb up, slide down, and become the ultimate slide champion!', 'On PC WASD ndash Move Mouse ndash Camera control Space ndash Jump On Mobile Use the on-screen controls Drag anywhere on the screen ndash Camera control', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Candy Quest', 2385, 'Candy Quest: A Sweet Puzzle Adventure! Candy Quest is an exciting and addictive logic-based puzzle game that will challenge your thinking while delivering endless fun. With vibrant visuals, engaging gameplay, and strategic challenges, it keeps players entertained for hours. Your mission is simple but requires skill and planning: collect the required number of blocks in each level, ranging from two to four different types. But don&amp;rsquo;t be fooled by its simplicity&amp;mdash;each level comes with a limited number of moves, making every decision crucial. Unlike many puzzle games, Candy Quest gives you unlimited access to powerful boosters, ensuring a thrill', 'PC controls Mouse Touch Control works on all browsers and all mobile devices', 'English'),
('Ocean Blast Match 3', 2386, 'Ocean King Match Puzzle is design based on ocean creatures to gives you the taste of ocean. For Match 3 puzzle game lovers to experience the ocean life in Game play. Match 3 items to start the fun and explore the ocean. Blast through multiple items Become the King of Ocean by matching and solving ocean puzzle. Show your matching and solving skills to unlock the depths of the ocean. Thousands of Brain storming puzzle to boost your brain cells. Ocean King Match Puzzle Gives you the chance to explore the hidden treasures of the ocean. Rule the ocean and show your skills to the world. Make your path to the end of bottom.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Shuffle Sage', 2387, 'Shuffle Sage &amp;ndash; A Solitaire Challenge of Wisdom and Strategy Step into the world of Shuffle Sage, a solitaire-inspired card game where patience meets mastery. Your goal is simple yet challenging: arrange the sequence of cards in perfect order, carefully alternating between red and black suits as you build your stacks. Every move counts &amp;mdash; place the wrong card and you&amp;rsquo;ll block your progress, but with the right foresight and planning, you can untangle the toughest layouts. Test your wisdom, sharpen your strategy, and prove yourself worthy of the title Shuffle Sage. Are you ready to conquer the deck and achieve the perfect sequence?', 'Arrange the cards as in Solitaire', 'English'),
('Bear Block Puzzle', 2388, 'Fun Bear Block Puzzle is a classic and engaging block puzzle game that challenges your logic and sharpens your mind. Designed for players of all ages, this game offers a perfect blend of relaxation and brain training, making it an excellent choice for puzzle lovers. With simple drag-and-drop mechanics, your goal is to place blocks on the grid and clear lines to earn points. Whether you are looking for a stress-relieving game, a logic challenge, or just a fun way to pass time, Fun Bear Block Puzzle is the perfect companion. How to Play Drag and drop blocks onto the 8x8 grid. Fill rows or columns completely to clear them and score points.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Deep Fuel', 2389, 'In Deep Fuel, you dive underground with your drill machine and race against fuel consumption. Collect gold, oil, and gems to boost your score, while avoiding walls and running out of fuel. Compete with AI bots, unlock upgrades, and climb the leaderboard. Simple controls, addictive gameplay, endless digging fun!', 'Arrow Keys A D rarr Move left amp right Down Arrow rarr Drill deeper auto-move down is also active Mouse Touch rarr Tap left or right side of the screen to move on mobile E Key Tap Button rarr Use active power-up', 'English'),
('Journey Of Escape', 2390, 'Escape games have always been a popular genre among puzzle enthusiasts and adventure seekers. They challenge players to think critically, solve intricate puzzles, and uncover hidden secrets while racing against time. Journey of Escape is an immersive collection of escape games designed to test your intelligence', 'Use mouse to play', 'English'),
('Red Ball Html5', 2391, 'The Red Ball HTML5 game captures players with its straightforward approach. Youll quickly see why its easy rules lead to so much replay value. This classic arcade fun is always ready to go, no matter where you are. It proves that great games dont need fancy graphics to be super entertaining. Its basic design hides a deep sense of fun. You get hooked trying to solve each levels unique puzzles. This game shows how simple ideas can deliver endless hours of fun. Why do people keep coming back for more? Its charm is tough to beat.', 'Use the arrow keys to play For mobile devices use the arrows that appear on the screen of your device', 'English'),
('Dead Seek', 2392, 'Dive into an explosive action-packed arcade where every shot is a fight for survival! Face relentless zombie hordes using a wide arsenal of weapons and upgrade them for maximum firepower. Discover new tactics and explore dangerous zones crawling with the infected. With vibrant graphics, thrilling gameplay, and non-stop action, theres never a dull moment. Are you ready to take on the challenge and survive the walking dead?', 'Shooting zombies is automatic Desktop Use WASD keys to move Mobile Use the on-screen controls', 'English'),
('Formula Go', 2393, 'Get behind the wheel of a high-speed Formula 1 car and challenge clever AI competitors on detailed tracks modeled after famous real-world circuits. Formula Go offers thrilling racing with responsive controls, intense competition, and a focus on driving skill. Fine-tune your vehicle, navigate sharp bends, and push your limits to secure a top spot on the podium.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tank Attack 2', 2394, 'Ready, warrior. Tank Attack will bring you to the most explosive battlefield ever. Control your tank and straight into chaos! Your goal is to attack, destroy and survive. Use your cannon to shoot at the enemys tanks and take advantage of the terrain to avoid their attacks. Simple controls, epic action, perfect for every boy who loves driving games!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Tung Tung Tung Sahur VS Bombardino Crocodilo', 2395, 'The two greatest enemies meet on a long road. Although one is strong, the others powerful stick blows are breaking through the air. Will you be able to carry the true hero to victory?', 'W or Up Arrow or Spacebar or Slide up for jump D or Right Arrow or Slide right for right A or Left Arrow or Slide reft for left Left Mouse Button or Fire Button for throw bat', 'English'),
('Otr Off Road Driving', 2396, 'Love car games and a true off-road driving adventure? In OTR Off-road Driving, you will have a real vehicle simulation experience. Enter off-road mode, choose different levels to start your challenge. Challenge your driving skills in the mountains. Work your way up the steep hill to your destination. Enter the Flyover Bridge Mode, control your car to the bullseye and win. Pay attention to finish the task within the time.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Shape Shifting: Race Game', 2397, 'Shape Shifting will take you across of all environment: land, air, sea To conquer them, you have to adapt quickly through all these environments Game Features - Transformable characters - Beautiful graphic design and relaxing soundtrack - Many exciting levels - Satisfying and addictive game-play', '- Transform the character to suit the environment - Make sure you choose the right one to become the winner - The higher level it is the more difficult game-play it is', 'English'),
('Ball Jumping', 2398, 'Bouncing ball is a great entertainment for fans of old games. This project is a kind of reincarnation of the old mobile ball games. The game is waiting for you: Classic platform gameplay Beautiful graphics Responsive and clear direction Come in and start playing! Complete the levels, collect rewards and train your reaction! Its all in the game.', 'You start at the bottom of the level your task is to go up When the ball pushes off the wall it changes direction Use this to successfully complete the levels Good luck', 'English'),
('COD Duty Call FPS', 2399, 'Step into the war-torn battlefield in COD Duty Call FPS, a fast-paced first-person shooter that throws players into the heart of modern warfare. Set in a near-future conflict, you assume the role of an elite special forces operative deployed across volatile regions, urban warzones, and covert enemy facilities in a campaign filled with explosive action and immersive storytelling. COD Duty Call FPS delivers an adrenaline-fueled experience where your reflexes, tactics, and precision will determine survival. The game features a gripping single-player campaign that follows a high-stakes mission to prevent global catastrophe. As a member of Shado', 'WASD - move Space - jump mouse - aim and shoot shift - run', 'English'),
('Punching Excavator: Breakdown!', 2400, 'Control a realistic excavator with detailed physics of movement and manipulation. Complete tasks of varying difficulty, from simple one-story constructions to complex multi-story buildings. Get rewards for each successfully completed level and invest your earnings in improving your equipment or cosmetic improvements to your character.', 'Motion Control W Forward movement S Backward movement A Move left D Move to the right Use the mouse wheel to rotate the sphere smoothly Mobile version Joystick to move Slider to change the rotation angle', 'English'),
('Idle Game Prison Life', 2401, 'Ever dreamed of running your prison? Now&amp;rsquo;s your chance! In this casual idle simulator, you&amp;rsquo;ll create a high-security prison empire. Upgrade and expand until you are on your way to becoming a tycoon! Create the perfect prison layout with cells, kitchens, gyms, and surveillance! Recruit guards, medics, and more to keep things under control.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cake Sorting Deluxe', 2402, 'Cake Sorting Deluxe is a fun and relaxing puzzle game that challenges your sorting skills! Shift cakes across shelves to make matches of three or more. Clear the board, uncover hidden and shadowed cakes, and solve tricky puzzles as you go. With cute visuals, smooth gameplay, and lots of sweet challenges, Cake Sorting Deluxe is a treat for anyone who loves a good puzzle. Ready to mix, match, and clear the shelves?', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to shift the cakes across the shelves Uncover hidden and shadowed cakes to complete each level and move on to the next sweet puzzle', 'English'),
('Bffs Kidcore Outfits', 2403, 'Welcome to Bffs Kidcore Outfits. Kidcore is an aesthetic that centers around bright colors, icons from the 90s, and kiddy themes. These young girls are very excited to try this fashion. Join as a fashion expert and browse the wardrobe for cute outfits. Pick a suitable one for each girl and give a unique hairstyle to them. Play these new dress-up games for girls at cutedressup.com', 'Left mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'English'),
('Pac Ring Adventure PRO', 2404, 'Pac Ring Adventure Pro is a thrilling twist on the classic Pacman experience! Navigate a fast-paced circular maze as Pacman chomps through glowing dots while dodging relentless enemies that patrol the ring. With tight turns, shifting speeds, and strategic movement, every second counts in this action-packed arcade adventure. Stay sharp, collect power-ups, and see how long you can survive the ring of danger! Key Features: Unique circular maze design for a fresh Pacman challenge Dodge and outmaneuver clever enemies on the ring Collect dots and power-ups to boost your score Fast, fluid gameplay with increasing difficulty', 'Click tap to change direction of pacman', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Draw Bridge Puzzle: Brain Game', 2405, 'Draw Bridge Puzzle - Draw Game is an exciting and challenging brain game that will put your problem-solving skills to the test. In this bridge-building adventure, your task is to draw paths for the car to safely navigate through obstacles and reach its destination. Get ready to embark on a thrilling journey of bridge construction and puzzle-solving as you draw roads to rescue the stranded car!', '- Touch the screen to start drawing - Hold and drag across to make the shapes you want - Once you finish release your finger and the car will run', 'English'),
('Toca Avatar My House', 2406, 'Welcome to Toca Avatar My House, a casual simulation game where you arrange your own house in the gaming world. If you are a Toca Boca enthusiast, try this life simulator game. You will find more pleasure living in a lovely house designed and decorated by yourself! Click on any of the items and drag to move them to any place you want. Put things in order, categorize cooking utensils, fill the cats bowl with food...', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Off road motocross', 2407, 'Off-road motocross is an exciting world of speed and adrenaline. Take a ride on dangerous tracks, overcome obstacles and upgrade your vehicles to become the king of the road. Drive a powerful motorcycle, perform stunts and improve your skills in an exciting racing game. Feel the speed and freedom while playing this addictive game.', 'In the game you control a motorcycle maintaining balance and control over it by pressing the buttons W and S or the up and down arrows To speed up the motorcycle use A and D or the left and right arrows to overcome various obstacles and get to the', 'English'),
('Level Rotator', 2408, 'The game is about a single ball that is located at the beginning of the pipe. Help him reach the end. Here you control not the ball, but all the levels at once! Try to reach the end by avoiding various obstacles along the way. In the game you will find: Memorable levels Intuitive operation Good graphics Just relax and turn on the game. Meditate and complete simple levels! Have a good game!', 'Relax and get into the game Start passing the first level you need to control the level you can do this using the mouse or keyboard Complete the levels and get rewards Go ahead', 'English'),
('Childcare Master Online', 2409, 'Get ready to become a parenting superstar in Childcare Master Online! This wonderful casual simulation game is all about playing the role of a top parenting expert. As soon as you start the game, youll find yourself in a lively daycare center with adorable kids. Whats your mission? Give them love and care! First, you need to create a warm environment.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sweet And Fruity Makeup', 2410, 'Indulge your senses in our makeup games sweet and fruity world! Immerse yourself in a vibrant palette of colors inspired by juicy fruits that will leave you looking fresh and fabulous. From luscious watermelon pinks to zesty lemon yellows and tangy orange hues, this game allows you to experiment with a selection of deliciously scented cosmetics. Create stunning looks using fruity lip glosses, shimmering eyeshadows, and blushes that mimic the radiant glow of ripe berries. Let your imagination run wild as you mix and match fruity fragrances, adding a delightful touch of freshness to your final touch.', 'Use your mouse to play this game on a desktop tap to play on mobile devices', 'English'),
('Bus Jam Escape', 2411, 'Bus Jam Escape is a fun and colorful puzzle game where your goal is to sort passengers into buses of the same color. Simply tap and send passengers to the appropriate bus, but watch the difficulty increase as new colors and obstacles appear.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Mr Autofire', 2412, 'Get ready to blast away endless alien hordes in this non-stop retro action shooter! The fabric of reality is in shreds and monsters are pouring in! Become Mr. Autofire and bring your biggest gun and your A game, because you&amp;rsquo;re the&amp;hellip; Defender of Everything! Rampage through levels, unlock new worlds and shoot the alien in the face. Discover new, more powerful weapons and gear. Get faster, nastier and more dodgier with different perks! It&amp;rsquo;s a you vs. everyone else situation, and it would be nasty to be everyone else. What are you waiting for? BITE THE BULLET AND RUMBLE!', 'Use the keyboard Mouse or Touch to play', 'English'),
('Falcon Dogfight', 2413, 'A balance between realism and exhilaration: Based on the dynamic design of real fighter jets, but simplifying complex operations, allowing players to quickly immerse themselves in the excitement of high-speed dogfighting and beyond visual range killing. Unlock top tier fighter jets such as F-22 Raptor, Su-27, and Su-33. BVR Showdown: Radar Lock, Automatic Tail Bite, Winning from Dozens of Kilometers Away.', 'Desktop w s pitch a d yaw q e roll hit radar is reset yaw pitch roll Mobile use joystick fireweapon hit weapon icon', 'English'),
('Pentaword', 2414, 'Guess the hidden five-letter word in just six tries! Use logic, spelling, and word skills in this brain teaser. Can you crack the Pentaword?', 'Your goal is to guess the hidden 5-letter word in 6 tries or less After each guess the tiles will change color to show how close your guess was Green ndash Correct letter in the correct spot Yellow ndash Correct letter in the wrong spot Gray amp n', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Logic Islands', 2415, 'A logic puzzle game inspired by Nurikabe and Islands of Insight. Create islands with exact numbers while keeping walls connected. Navigate through 6 unique worlds with different rulesets - from Classic Nurikabe to advanced mechanics like Yin-Yang connectivity. Each world introduces new challenges with ice blocks, one-way arrows, and special orb mechanics across 240 hand-picked puzzles.', 'On PC Click to toggle cells between island wall Double-click or Ctrl click to fill connected areas Mouse wheel or Space to switch draw modes Z to undo R to restart On mobile Tap to toggle Double-tap to fill areas', 'English'),
('Crazy Color Balls 2', 2416, 'Crazy Color Balls 2 is an amazing and exciting next-level game very similar to what is Crazy Color Balls. Rush your way through and around obstacles of all shapes and sizes in this colorful game! Control the color ball and try to avoid hitting any objects that are not the same color as the ball. The speed of the game starts slow and picks up fast as the game progresses. In this version of game, the levels grow easier to much tougher and are much more fun to clear. Have lotta fun!', 'Avoid ball hitting other colors', 'English'),
('Stop Zombies', 2417, 'Armed with a blaster that fires colored projectiles, you must hold your ground against a relentless horde in Stop Zombies. Each undead creature can only be taken down with a bullet matching its color, so quick thinking and sharp reflexes are your best defense. As the swarm grows stronger, your survival depends on staying alert and firing smart to prevent the apocalypse from reaching you.', 'Use Keyboard for desktop and Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Tile Stamper', 2418, 'Looking for a fun and casual game that&amp;rsquo;s satisfying and addictive? Tile Stamper is a super uptempo tile floor laying management game! Let you create the most perfect floor with happy clicking! Control your character to place each tile with precision and fill the floor perfectly. Continuously upgrade your vehicles to increase efficiency.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('OrbitDefense', 2419, 'Protect the planet from collision. When your finger presses down on the screen, the ball spins and destroys the object crashing into the planet.Come and play and see how many points you get.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Bob the Builder Coloring', 2420, 'Bob the Builder Coloring: Creative Fun for Little Artists. Fun online coloring game designed just for kids who love creativity, colors and cartoons! Join Bob and his trusty crew in this colorful adventure where imagination is the only limit. Pick your favorite scenes, grab your virtual crayons, and start painting! Whether you want to follow the original colors or mix things up with wild rainbow designs, this game lets you be the artist. It is perfect for little builders who want to relax, have fun, and bring their favorite characters to life&amp;mdash;one brushstroke at a time. No mess, no rules, just loads', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Tricky Arrow 2', 2421, 'In this precision-shooting game, your skills will be put to the test as you aim to hit a spinning circle target with perfect accuracy. However, the challenge doesnt end there, as you must also avoid other arrows flying towards you, making each moment a thrilling puzzle to solve. With simple yet addictive gameplay, this game is perfect for players of all ages who enjoy a good reflex-testing challenge. Your aim and quick reflexes will be put to the limit as you navigate through the twists and turns of this game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Data Breach', 2422, 'Youre a Computer Virus, are you strong enough to avoid every scanner the antivirus throws at you? Lets find out in Data Breach!!', 'Space Bar or Left Click to jump', 'English'),
('Monster Rush cat', 2423, 'Monster Rush Cat is a fast-paced arcade game where you launch a cute monster-cat to catch spinning candies in the sky. Time your jumps perfectly, collect coins, and avoid falling to your doom! As you progress, the challenge increases with moving targets and tricky timing. Unlock new monster skins and aim for the highest score in this colorful, one-tap skill game!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('BlockBreaker', 2424, 'The most fun block-playing game. Shoot the small balls to hit the bricks. After hitting other balls, the number of balls shot each time will increase. After hitting the bricks, energy will be collected. When the energy is full, you can directly eliminate a row of bricks. Come and give it a try', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Chicken Dash', 2425, 'Chicken Dash is a fun and fast platform game where you help a little chicken run and jump its way to the finish line. Each level is full of tricky obstacles, and you need to time your jumps perfectly to avoid them. Along the way, collect shiny coins to boost your score. It&amp;rsquo;s a simple and exciting adventure that&amp;rsquo;s perfect for all ages!', 'Desktop Up Arrow Jump Right Arrow Move Forward Click and Drag Move the Chicken Mobile Tap Right Side Move Tap and swipe up Jump', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur Supermarket', 2426, 'Tung Tung Sahur has started running a supermarket. He got a job as a cashier in a busy store. Italian brainrot characters come to shop, but don&amp;rsquo;t let them make a mess! Clean the floor immediately to keep the store spotless. You also need to manage the cash register&amp;mdash;don&amp;rsquo;t keep customers waiting too long. Make sure to scan every item&amp;rsquo;s barcode to track how many products leave the store. If the shelves start to empty, use the money you&amp;rsquo;ve earned to restock from the storage room.', 'Use the WASD keys to move To clean the floor grab a broom from the storage room After sweeping rinse the broom in the water bucket Scan the barcodes of purchased items and place them in the shopping basket Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English'),
('BottleFlip', 2427, 'Test your timing and reflexes in this fun fruit-flipping challenge! Be careful not to let the fruits store obstacles. See how many points you can achieve!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Black And Pink', 2428, 'Avoid the balls while trying to connect all the sides to fill it in black or pink according to what the level desires. Each time a level is cleared, the ball count is doubled and the game becomes harder and harder.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tennis Dash', 2429, 'Tennis Dash is a fast and fun game where a cute cat plays tennis like a pro! The tennis ball comes from different directions, and your job is to move the cat left and right to hit it. Be quick&amp;mdash;if you miss the ball three times, the game is over! It&amp;rsquo;s easy to play but really hard to master. Try to beat your own high score and keep the rally going!', 'Desktop Click and Drag Left or Right Move the Cat bear Mobile Tap and drag Left or Right Move the Cat bear', 'English'),
('Spirit Boy', 2430, 'In this clever puzzle adventure, you guide a boy through tricky levels filled with deadly traps and clever challenges. Spirit Boy transforms into a ghostly soul when faced with danger, letting him float past spikes and reach hidden areas. But to finish the level, he must return to his human form and find the exit door all while guarding his three precious lives.', 'Use Mouse and Keyboard for desktop Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Mysterious Familiars Enchanted Bestiary', 2431, 'Welcome to the magical world of Mysterious Familiars! Discover the Witchcraft Encyclopedia full of mysterious and cute creatures. Your task is to fill the magic vessel by simply tapping on the screen. Each click fills the potion bowl. As soon as the vessel is filled, a new image of one of the familiars or its next stage of maturation will open. Explore magical locations, from the Moonlight Glade to the Slug Trail, and watch incredible creatures appear from small drops of magic potion. Do you want to speed up the process? Trade clicks for upgrades and increase your click power. Collect the entire encyclopedia and become a true expert on magical creatures! Start the adventure right now - the familiars are waiting for you!', 'Depending on the gaming device either a click of a computer mouse or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it', 'English'),
('Drive Mad 2', 2432, 'Want to begin a wildly exciting driving challenge? Welcome to Drive Mad 2, the craziest 3D driving simulation adventure youve ever seen. Youll be racing your sports car around many strange and dangerous tracks! There are all kinds of traps and mechanisms here. For example, sledgehammers, bottles, windmills, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cosmic Strike 2.0', 2433, 'A game where you can explore space and battle spaceships. Come on, head into space and fight against extremely tough bosses. What happened, are you scared? There are 3 long levels in the game and each level has a boss with its own different gameplay. As you destroy enemies and bosses, you earn money and can buy new ships. Each ships different damage and firing style make the game different. And last boss is not broken it has a weak spot.', 'W to acceleration S to slow Left Click to Fire Move with mouse f a ship crashs you you die also', 'English'),
('Hidden Hero', 2434, 'Help Lily Escape the Cat Chaos! Join Lily on a fast-paced adventure as she dashes, jumps, and ducks to dodge an endless wave of mischievous cats! These fluffy troublemakers are everywhere&amp;mdash;falling from the sky, popping out of trash cans, and even riding skateboards! Use quick reflexes and power-ups to survive as long as you can. Cute, chaotic, and full of surprises, Cat Dodge: Lilys Run is the purr-fect mix of fun and challenge. Can you keep Lily safe and climb the leaderboard?', 'Mouse or finger click or tap to play tap to hide behind something', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Italian Brainrot Puzzle', 2435, 'In the game Italian Brainrot Puzzle you have 16 puzzles with pictures of Italian Brainrot characters. Assemble them by shifting to position the pieces.To change drag parts up to another position. Complete a level, go to the next. In each level you have limited time for which you need to complete it. Enjoy this game!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Screw Pin Jam Puzzle', 2436, 'Screw Pin Jam Puzzle is an incredibly creative and strategic puzzle game designed to enhance players spatial imagination and strategic planning abilities. In this game, players face a board composed of complex and intricately placed screws and pins. Each screw and pin could be key to solving the puzzle, requiring careful consideration with every move. Game features include: Diverse level designs: Ranging from simple to complex, each level has a unique layout and difficulty, requiring players to constantly adjust their solution strategies. Intuitive interface: Clear graphics and smooth animation make it easy for players to pick up, while', 'Mouse Controls', 'English'),
('Stickman Rescue Draw 2 Save', 2437, 'Your brain is the only shield for the stickman! Enjoy a super casual puzzler in the Stickman Rescue - Draw 2 Save. Use your finger to draw lines and save the stickman from danger! In each level, the stickman is in trouble, such as falling rocks, flying arrows, deep pits, etc. It&amp;rsquo;s up to you to draw a safe shield, a bridge, or a clever device to keep him safe and complete your rescue mission!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tumble Boat', 2438, 'Tumble Boat is a fun and tricky puzzle game where your goal is to land a boat safely on the ground. The boat starts on top of a stack of blocks, and you have to remove the blocks one by one without tipping the tower. Be careful&amp;mdash;if the boat falls, the game is over! Each level brings a new challenge that will test your thinking and timing.', 'Desktop Mouse Click and drag Remove a Block Mobile Tap and drag Remove a Block', 'English'),
('Duck Shift', 2439, 'Try to pass all the duck tests on each level avoiding danger in the Duck Shift game. Use your wits to take the key from the door and find the right way to it. But be prepared to deftly jump over deadly spikes otherwise your path will start from the beginning of the level.', 'Use Keyboard for desktop and Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Super Mano  Run Blast and Slash', 2440, 'Join Super Mano in a high-octane, Mario-inspired adventure where action meets strategy! Armed with guns, swords, and explosive bombs, Mano must battle waves of quirky enemies, overcome tricky traps, and defeat the forces of evil threatening his colorful pixel world. This side-scrolling platformer combines nostalgic retro charm with thrilling combat mechanics. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re jumping on platforms or blasting through bosses, Super Mano delivers non-stop arcade-style fun for gamers of all ages!', 'Move Left larr Arrow Move Right rarr Arrow Move Up e g ladder or elevator uarr Arrow Move Down e g crouch drop darr Arrow Jump Spacebar Shoot Gun F Throw Bomb G Fly Jetpack Glide T Melee Attack Sword Punch C', 'English'),
('Labubu Skate Parkour', 2441, 'Labubu must survive the sky course! Help Labubu reach the finish line safely. Be careful you could fall from the sky or crash into obstacles and lose. Collect all the gold coins and make it to the finish line in one piece!', 'Use the WASD keys to move Double jump available Playable on both mobile and PC Collect all the gold coins and reach the finish line', 'English'),
('Blockfall Blitz: Master the Falling Blocks!', 2442, 'Blockfall Blitz is a fast-paced, addictive puzzle game inspired by classic falling block titles. Strategically place descending tetrominoes to complete and clear horizontal lines. Race against the clock as the blocks fall faster with every line you clear. Plan ahead using the Next Piece preview and outsmart the grid by utilizing the new Hold Piece feature! How many lines can you clear and how high can you score before the blocks reach the top?', 'Move Piece Keyboard Left Arrow larr Right Arrow rarr Touch Swipe Left Swipe Right on the game board Rotate Piece Keyboard Up Arrow uarr Touch Tap on the game board Soft Drop Move Down Faster Keyboard Down Arrow darr Touch', 'English'),
('Nailong Rush Run', 2443, 'Nailong Rush Run is a fun 3D parkour game that brings you into a wonderful world. You will play as a cute dinosaur running on an endless platform. You need to keep collecting more nailongs and expanding your team! Increase your number through positive number gates. Lead your team to avoid various obstacles like roadblocks, vehicles, etc. Reach the finish line and start fighting with the enemy dinosaurs.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Birdy Trip', 2444, 'You are not alone in the sky! It&amp;rsquo;s time to migrate to sunny lands. Grab your cute friends on the way and be careful, many dangers could smash you during your journey. Features: &amp;bull; One-Touch control &amp;bull; Enjoy an original atmosphere &amp;amp; colorful graphics &amp;bull; Discover &amp;amp; catch more than 8 birds &amp;bull; Complete dozens of missions &amp;bull; Beware of eagles!', 'Use the Mouse or Touch to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Treat Tumble', 2445, 'Match. Munch. Mayhem! Dive into a deliciously addictive world of candy-coated chaos in Treat Tumble &amp;mdash; the ultimate match-3 puzzle adventure! Swap and match colorful treats like gummy bears, chocolate bites, and jelly cubes to clear levels and unlock sweet surprises. With 100+ vibrant levels, explosive power-ups, and daily rewards, Treat Tumble is your perfect sugar rush &amp;mdash; no calories included! Game Features: Match-3 Magic &amp;ndash; Match 3 or more treats to blast through obstacles and earn tasty combos! Whimsical Worlds &amp;ndash; Explore candy kingdoms, soda swamps, and cookie cliffs.', 'Match-3 and get heavy bonuses', 'English'),
('Rolling Going Balls', 2446, 'Its time to push your reflexes to the limit. Rolling Going Balls is an addictive 3D platform rolling game where you take charge of a fast-moving ball. Rolling and running through tricky tracks full of twists and traps! Smooth rolling controls to guide your ball with precision! Collect as many balls as you can along the way to boost your level! Watch out! Avoid dangerous obstacles like spikes, pendulums, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Italian animals with voice acting', 2447, 'All Italian animals and their original sounds are here! In the game, you can open all the characters from the meme about Italian animals and listen to their voice acting with an interesting fusion mechanic. Ballerina Cappuccino and Bombardino Crocodilo are already waiting for you!', '1 Click on the animals to get coins 2 Buy Italian animals for coins 3 Combine the same character to get the next level Italian animal 4 Reach the last character', 'English'),
('BallRun', 2448, 'Choose the correct route to make the turn. The game will randomly generate routes, each route corresponds to a color, by controlling the character to choose the same color with the character of the route to turn, enter the new route after the characters color will randomly change. Each time you choose the correct route you will get one point, so try and see how many points you can get.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Geometry Flap', 2449, 'Enter a world of bold outlines, sharp corners, and pure reflex. In Geometry Flap, you control a shapeshifting arrow darting through a black-and-white maze of geometric chaos. Tap to flap, weave through deadly gates, and dodge precision traps in this high-speed gauntlet of skill. Features: One mistake = instant crash. Simple to play, brutally hard to master. Unlock dozens of slick arrow skins. Will you survive the rhythm of geometry? Challenge your reflex. Flap to glory.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Trump Wheelie Challenge', 2450, 'Trump Wheelie Challenge is a super fun 2D game where you drive a jeep on one wheel! Balance carefully, collect money, jump over bouncing balls, and try to reach the finish line without flipping over. Complete each level by mastering the wheelie and surviving the chaos! Play the Trump Wheelie Challenge game now.', 'Right Arrow or mouse', 'English'),
('Hard Path', 2451, 'Brace yourself for a wild and unpredictable journey as you help a clumsy hero stumble through complex 2D labyrinths packed with traps, tricks, and unexpected turns. Hard Path delivers a blend of comedy and challenge, turning every step into a potential disaster or triumph. Navigate tight corners, dodge bizarre hazards, and try to keep the Warrior on track in this chaotic maze-filled adventure.', 'Use Keyboard for desktop and Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Super Ball Juggling Remix', 2452, 'Super Ball Juggling Remix is a fast-paced arcade game where you juggle a soccer ball without letting it drop &amp;mdash; but with a twist! Travel across iconic locations like Paris, New York, Rome, Pisa, and Sydney, showcasing your freestyle skills in stunning backdrops. Simple to play, hard to master, and packed with global style &amp;mdash; how long can you keep the ball in the air?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Drive Zone', 2453, 'Dive into a world of speed and thrill! This game takes you on a ride through city streets, rally tracks, and wild off-road terrains. Feel the power of the engines, master every turn, and unleash your inner racer. Its not just about speed &amp;mdash; its about freedom, challenge, and the rush of the unknown. Are you ready to become a legend on every surface?', 'Desktop W - Accelerator S - Brake Reverse A - Left D - Right C - Camera Switch Esc - Pause Mobile Use on-screen controls', 'English'),
('Undead Appetite', 2454, 'Undead Appetite Run. Dodge. Survive the hunger of the dead. In Undead Appetite, the world has fallen &amp;mdash; and now theyre coming. Flesh-hungry zombies, spinning saws, and flying bullets stand between you and survival in this high-intensity action game where every second counts. Navigate through chaotic battlegrounds filled with traps and undead horrors. Stay on the move, dodge the danger, and outlast the apocalypse. With only your reflexes and instincts, you must survive the insatiable appetite of the undead.', 'Use Z and X to jump and fire', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Peaceful Gardening', 2455, 'A relaxing game where you plant flowers and watch nature come alive. Add butterflies, toggle rain, and create a peaceful digital garden.', 'Mouse Tap', 'English'),
('break it', 2456, 'Unleash your fury in BREAK IT, a fast-paced action game where an angry fuzzy creature breaks through walls with sheer foot power! Take control of a mischievous Labubu-style hero on a vertical descent through layers of obstacles, spikes, and breakable bricks. Your mission: smash everything in your path &amp;mdash; but be careful not to hit the deadly spikes or unbreakable blocks!', 'Hold Left Mouse Button Smash downward Release Stop smashing to avoid obstacles', 'English'),
('Tap to Fish', 2457, 'Cast your line, reel in the rewards, and grow your fishing empire! In Tap to Fish, you begin with simple gear and work your way up by catching and selling fish for gold. Every catch earns you coins to upgrade your fishing rod boosting its capacity and reaching deeper waters. With its smooth gameplay and vibrant visuals, this hypercasual adventure is easy to pick up and hard to put down.', 'Use Mouse for desktop and Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Kids Toy Set Mobile', 2458, 'Welcome to Kid Toy Set Mobile, a collection of casual mini-games especially for girls. You can find various relaxing games here, including doll dress-up, doctor simulator, makeover game, matching game, pop it game, and so on. Your goal is to get fully relaxed and remove all pressure from a busy day. Select one level that interests you and begin to play!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Bank Boom Tung Tung Sahur', 2459, 'Are you ready for a bank heist? You have 20 seconds to crack the safe! Compete with your friend &amp;mdash; the first to open the vault wins. Smash the safe open and beat your friend to it. Hit your friend with a club to slow them down and win the race. The club is a powerful weapon. The fate of the game is in your hands. Strike fast and unlock the bank vault!', 'bull Move using WASD or the Arrow Keys bull Press S or the Down Arrow to swing the club bull Playable on both mobile and PC bull Stand on the vault for 20 seconds to open it and win the game', 'English'),
('Geometry Dash Unblocked', 2460, 'GeometryDashUnblocked is a fun sidescrolling action arcade rush. Control the geometric cubes through a large number of spikes. Seize the moment and tap to jump so that the cube avoids collisions and survives longer. Challenge the farthest distance to get a high score! Unlock more funny skins to participate in the challenge and give you a different experience!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Labubu Gokart', 2461, 'Labubu started the engine and slammed the pedal to the metal! You have to help him. Guide Labubu out of the garage and all the way to the finish line. Try to collect all the fuel cans along the way. Be careful &amp;mdash; there are plenty of obstacles waiting on the road. And it&amp;rsquo;s not just obstacles&amp;hellip; bombs are falling from the sky too! Watch out for everything and make sure Labubu reaches the finish line in one piece.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Double jump available Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English'),
('Bloxorz', 2462, 'Bloxorz is a block sliding puzzle game. You will need roll the block around the board until it falls into the square hole in 33 challenging levels.', 'WASD or Arrow keys to roll the block - Space bar to switch between the blocks', 'English'),
('Block Breaker: Miner Quest', 2463, 'Tap, Dash, Survive! Dive into the depths in Miner Dash: Endless Escape! Smash through blocks, dodge falling rocks, and gather as many gold coins as you can. Unlock epic new skins and test your reflexes in this fast-paced, endless adventure. Are you fast enough to beat your own record? Features: Addictive endless gameplay Simple tap-to-move controls Challenging obstacles and traps Unlockable miner skins Leaderboard support (if applicable)', 'Tap Left Right to move the miner Auto-mine blocks in your path Avoid falling rocks ndash they end your run Collect coins to unlock new characters', 'English'),
('The War2727', 2464, 'This is a turn-based casual game with a samurai theme based on my previous game.If you like this kind of game, I will continue to update the content!', 'Click or touch', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Car Simulation Drive Master', 2465, 'Welcome to Car Park Simulator! Are you ready to put your driving skills to the ultimate test? Tackle 72 challenging levels packed with tight spaces, tricky obstacles, and realistic parking scenarios. Master precision, timing, and control as you navigate your way to parking perfection!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Samurai Cow Man', 2466, 'Samurai Cow Man is a wild, action-packed adventure like no udder! Step into the hooves of a fearless cow with the heart of a samurai and the sword skills to match. Battle enemies, slash through obstacles, and defend your honor across epic landscapes. How to play: Slash, dodge, and dash using smooth touch controls. Fight off waves of enemies with powerful katana combos. Unlock new armor, weapons, and wild samurai abilities. Whether youre charging through bamboo forests or facing legendary bosses, every level is packed with humor, action, and unexpected surprises.', 'Use arrow key on keyboard', 'English'),
('House Cleaning ASMR', 2467, 'The house is in an extremely messy condition! Come help out with the cleaning work. House Cleaning ASMR is a casual simulation game where you can experience various kinds of cleaning work. For example, cleaning fans, wiping the dust off the wall, and doing handbag care. All the cleaning tasks are well-designed and highly interactive.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Same and Different Donut', 2468, 'Get ready to have some fun with the game Same &amp;amp; Different Donut! Take a close look at these delicious, colorful donuts. Can you spot which ones look exactly the same? Now, see if you can find the one that&amp;rsquo;s different from the rest. You&amp;rsquo;ll get to answer a few fun questions along the way. After that, it&amp;rsquo;s time to get creative and design your very own donut&amp;mdash;choose your favorite colors and toppings! And of course, don&amp;rsquo;t forget to pretend to take a big bite and &amp;ldquo;eat&amp;rdquo; your creation. Enjoy the game and have lots of fun!', 'mouse click or touch screen', 'English'),
('Hexa Puzzle Master', 2469, 'Hexa Puzzle Master is a fun and addictive web puzzle game where players fit hexagonal blocks into a grid. With simple drag-and-drop controls, players must think strategically to complete levels without gaps. Featuring multiple difficulty levels and a sleek design, the game offers a relaxing yet challenging experience for puzzle lovers of all ages!', 'Drag amp Drop ndash Click and drag hexagonal blocks to place them on the board Fill the Grid ndash Arrange the pieces to fit perfectly without leaving gaps No Rotation Needed ndash Blocks are pre-set in orientation so focus on placement No Tim', 'English'),
('Monster Truck Dirt Rally', 2470, 'Monster Truck Dirt Rally delivers high-octane, off-road racing action with powerful monster trucks tearing through rugged dirt tracks. Crush obstacles, perform insane stunts, and compete in adrenaline-fueled rally events. With realistic physics, dynamic environments, and customizable trucks. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.y8gamesx.com/''&gt;https://www.y8gamesx.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'WASD to drive', 'English'),
('CircleCrash', 2471, 'The control car is driving on the ring road.There will be other vehicles during the driving process, avoid collision with other vehicles.Coins are earned while driving, which can be used to unlock new vehicles.Come and experience it!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Gummy Blocks Puzzle', 2472, 'Gummy Blocks Puzzle is a block puzzle game where you drop pieces to form and eliminate complete lines on the screen, both vertically and horizontally. Just drag and position the blocks on the board to create lines. Its simple to play and immensely enjoyable! Embrace the challenge of arranging the pieces and observe the lines vanish as you advance. Ideal for a quick session to hone your puzzle abilities or for longer gaming periods.', 'Enjoy this cheerful rainbow-themed Gummy Blocks Puzzle game Slide the delicious gummy blocks into the empty spaces and eliminate rows and columns on the grid Challenge yourself to see how far you can progress while enhancing skills in planning mental', 'English'),
('Word Search Universe', 2473, 'Word Search Universe is a fun and relaxing puzzle game where you search for hidden words in a grid. The game has 20 chapters, and each one comes with easy, medium, and hard levels to match your skill. In every level, you need to find 6 hidden words. If you get stuck, you can use a hint to help you out. Its a great way to have fun, improve your vocabulary, and keep your brain sharp!', 'Tap and drag to highlight the hidden words in the grid Use the hint button if you need help finding a word', 'English'),
('Fruit Merge Juicy Drop Fun', 2474, 'Fruit Merge Drop Frenzy &amp;ndash; Juicy Merge, Match &amp;amp; Compete! Embark on a fruity adventure with Fruit Drop Fun! Dive into a vibrant world of colorful fruits, satisfying merges, and endless fun in the most addictive fruit merge game around. From luscious watermelons to juicy pineapples, Fruit Merge combine matching fruits to unlock higher-level combos and blast your way through exciting fruit puzzles. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a casual gamer or a puzzle pro, Fruit Drop Frenzy offers a perfect mix of strategy, relaxation, and challenge in this Juicy Merge Game!', 'Drop and merge fruits to create higher-level fruits and enjoy juicy combo fun', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('The Hidden Booty', 2475, 'The Hidden Booty Tap smart. Track clues. Find the treasure! Set sail on a puzzling pirate adventure in The Hidden Booty, a clever treasure-hunt game where intuition meets strategy. Your goal? Discover the hidden treasure buried beneath one of many mysterious cards &amp;mdash; before your moves run out! Tap on cards to reveal directional clues pointing toward the treasure. Each clue brings you closer, but choose wisely &amp;mdash; every tap counts! With a limited number of moves, every decision is critical. Can you outwit the map and uncover the legendary Hidden Booty?', 'Click guess and move based on shown arrows', 'English'),
('Cat Up', 2476, 'At first glance, this is a simple platformer with one button, but not everything is so simple. You have to control a small and very active pixel cat, who needs to overcome all 15 levels and collect all the coins to open all the doors.', 'Use Mouse for desktop and Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Light It Rush', 2477, 'Swing, jump, flip and slide your stickman flip master body from one neon color shape to another to make them glow and light-it up. It&amp;rsquo;s a dark world out there for a teeny little stickman flip master like you, and it&amp;rsquo;s about time you light-it up and make the colors glow.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hide And Seek Friends!', 2478, 'The good old classic hide &amp;amp; seek. Play either as a seeker or as a hider and build your shelters from cars or office desks, hide in the water, in the hay pile, in the cornfield, in the boss office and most importantly, push others in the seekers vision field. Try to be kind though. Hide N Seek! : Dive into the ultimate online Hide &amp;amp; Seek experience! Battle in real-time multiplayer matches across immersive, interactive worlds. Play as the cunning hider or relentless seeker. Outsmart rivals, master stealth or track with precision. Non-stop action, strategy, and global fun await!', 'Welcome to the world of Hide amp Seek 3D', 'English'),
('Super Motocross', 2479, 'Ride your dirt bike through challenging levels full of ramps, jumps, and obstacles. Balance, accelerate, and reach the finish line without crashing! A fun and fast-paced HTML5 motocross game for all ages.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('DIY Ice Cream Roll Cone', 2480, 'Summer is on its way! Dont you want to try a cool ice cream? What about delicious summer desserts? Welcome to DIY Ice Cream Roll Cone, a casual food DIY game for kids. Cool down with this ice cream dessert cooking simulation designed against the hot summer! If you are a girl who loves eating ice cream or a casual DIY gamer, join us and enjoy endless fun.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('VehicleFactory', 2481, 'VehicleFactory is a creative physics-based builder game where your engineering skills are put to the test! Construct your own vehicle by attaching components like wheels, special wheels, and ventilators. Once your design is ready, hit the Start button and watch your custom creation navigate a dynamic physics map. Will your build make it to the destination? Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesx.com/''&gt;https://www.crazygamesx.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Ketchup Mod', 2482, 'Sprunki Ketchup Mod - A game with physics of throws and ragdoll elements. Throw ketchup so as to get into the Sprunki and turn it into a ketchup version! Try your hand at 30 levels! The difficulty will increase, and the maps will increase. Think with your head: calculate the perfect trajectory of the throw and use the bounces to win!', 'Your mission throw ketchup at Simon Use the ketchup as a projectile stretch it like a slingshot and throw it accurately', 'English'),
('Sauce Silk Spy', 2483, 'Sauce Silk Spy: The Doomsday War of Shiba Inu Agent On the wasteland devoured by zombie viruses, a skilled Shiba Inu will shoulder the ultimate mission of saving humanity. When traditional doomsday themes encounter cute pet agents, a passionate and absurd breakout battle is about to begin!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('BlockPuzzleMagic', 2484, 'Assemble and eliminate the blocks. Various shaped blocks will randomly appear at the bottom. Drag the blocks into the upper box. They will be eliminated when a row or column is filled. Come and give it a try.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Slime Smile', 2485, 'Today is the story of Slime! Get a better clearance experience by matching attributes. If you like it, we will continue to update more content in the future!', 'Mouse click or touch', 'English'),
('CircleLeap', 2486, 'Control the arrow to sprint to the next circle. Seize the moment, so that the arrow sprint to avoid the vortex.Come and experience it and see how many points you can earn.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Zombies vs. Sunflowers', 2487, 'In this action-packed tower defense game, your garden is under siege by relentless zombies! Strategically place unique plants&amp;mdash;each with special abilities&amp;mdash;to stop the shambling invaders. Unlock &amp;amp; Upgrade &amp;ndash; Strengthen your plants to unleash powerful attacks and create an unbeatable defense. Face Fearsome Foes &amp;ndash; Battle waves of zombies, each with their own strengths and weaknesses. Earn Sun &amp;amp; Survive &amp;ndash; Collect resources to grow your arsenal and hold the line! Can you outsmart the undead and protect your home? The battle for survival begins now!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Dead Rails', 2488, 'Sprunki Dead Rails - protect the train! Cooperative survival against zombies with block building. To make the game easier, you can buy a turret that will help destroy zombies. Play on one of 6 maps. The maps themselves are huge! Play with a friend, or in single player mode. The game has 15 Sprunki skins for both players, as well as 12 different blocks. The game has 4 types of weapons: pistol, PP, AK-47, RPG.', 'On a mobile device controls are provided using on-screen buttons On PC - Blue player main bull Movement arrow keys larr rarr uarr darr bull Shoot J bull Build K - Red player bull Movement WASD bull Shoot F bull Build', 'English'),
('Truck Driving Simulator offroad', 2489, 'Experience the thrill of offroad trucking! Navigate rugged terrain, deliver cargo through challenging paths, and master powerful trucks in realistic environments. Conquer hills, mud, and rivers in this ultimate truck driving simulator adventure. Ready to drive? Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesonline.com/''&gt;https://www.crazygamesonline.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pixel Path', 2490, 'Help a brave pixel hero survive mind-bending levels filled with deadly traps, teleporters, and gravity-defying puzzles! Tap to flip the world upside-down, leap over spinning saws, and collect glittering gems to unlock thrilling new worlds. One wrong move&amp;mdash;and it&amp;rsquo;s game over!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Wicked Whirl', 2491, 'Wicked Whirl Enter the swirling chaos of Halloween in Wicked Whirl, the spookiest match-3 puzzle game of the season! Match haunted items like glowing pumpkins, creepy eyeballs, magic potions, and mischievous skulls to cast spells, break curses, and uncover hidden surprises. With every swipe, youll venture deeper into eerie forests, haunted mansions, and cursed graveyards. Can you survive the whirl of wicked challenges and unlock all the spooky secrets before midnight strikes?', 'Match-3 amp Win', 'English'),
('ThroneHold', 2492, 'The throne is lost. The castle is cursed. Take it back. In Thronehold, you step into the boots of a lone warrior trapped in a crumbling castle filled with danger, darkness, and long-forgotten secrets. This intense platformer combines fast-paced action, precision jumps, and clever traps set across a labyrinthine stronghold once ruled by kings &amp;mdash; now haunted by creatures of shadow. Leap over deadly spikes, scale ancient towers, unlock hidden paths, and fight your way through cursed knights, spectral beasts, and twisted machines guarding the throne room. Only the strongest can reclaim the Thronehold.', 'Avoid obstacles and keep moving Click to jump', 'English'),
('Survival Shooter Game', 2493, 'Survival Shooter is a fast-paced top-down action game where you must fight off endless waves of enemies. Armed with powerful weapons and quick reflexes, you&amp;rsquo;ll battle through intense arenas, collect power-ups, and unlock upgrades to survive as long as possible. The enemies get stronger, faster, and more aggressive&amp;mdash;only the skilled will last. With stylized visuals, responsive twin-stick controls, and challenging gameplay, Survival Shooter delivers an adrenaline-pumping experience that keeps you coming back for more. How long can you survive the onslaught? Climb the leaderboard and prove your worth in the ultimate survival test.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sweet Beasts', 2494, 'Match candy. Feed monsters. Unleash the sugar chaos! Step into the wild and whimsical world of Sweet Beasts, a candy-packed match-3 puzzle adventure where adorable monsters have an insatiable sweet tooth! Match colorful candies, trigger explosive combos, and feed your hungry beast buddies as you journey through gooey gumdrop forests, marshmallow mountains, and jelly lagoons. Each level brings new challenges and mischievous monster mayhem! Unlock new creatures, discover their candy-craving powers, and take on sticky obstacles in hundreds of deliciously tricky levels.', 'Match-3 and win', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Slime Rain', 2495, 'Dodge the falling objects and collect as many coins as you can! Fast-paced, reflex-based arcade game that&amp;rsquo;s easy to play but hard to master. How long can you survive?', 'Keyboard or slide or touch', 'English'),
('Thung Thung Sahur Playgrounds Escape', 2496, 'Thung Thung Sahur Playgrounds Escape is a survival horror. You must find a way to complete the quest with certain time before Thung Thung catch you!', 'wasd to move', 'English'),
('Drag N Boom', 2497, 'DragnBoom is a fun old-school arcade game combining speed and precision! &amp;bull; Dive into an imaginary medieval universe full of heroes, echoing the greatest arcade and platform games of all time.', 'Use the mouse or touch to play', 'English'),
('Parking Polly Cars', 2498, 'Get ready to master the ultimate car parking puzzle! In Parking Poly Cars, your mission is to escape traffic jams by moving the right cars in the right order. Enjoy addictive traffic jam puzzle gameplay that tests your logic and strategy. Slide the cars, unblock the path, and clear the parking lot in this fun and challenging car puzzle game! Perfect for fans of brain games, parking simulators, and traffic jam games. With increasing difficulty and smart levels, this car parking game will keep your brain sharp. Whether youre a casual player or a puzzle pro, enjoy hours of antistress fun!', 'Mouse Click and drag cars to move them Touch Tap and swipe cars on mobile to slide them', 'English'),
('Heroic Barrage', 2499, 'Unleash bullets. Dodge chaos. Defend the realm. In Heroic Barrage, you are the last line of defense&amp;mdash;a fearless warrior armed with endless firepower, facing wave after wave of relentless enemies. Set in a fast-paced side-scrolling battlefield just above ground level, this arcade-style adventure challenges your reflexes, accuracy, and courage. Enemies swarm from every direction and altitude. Your job? Shoot non-stop, survive the onslaught, and dominate the skies with precision and style. With intuitive joystick controls, you&amp;rsquo;ll move, aim, and blast through ever-increasing waves of flying foes.', 'Dodge enemies and shoot', 'English'),
('LinksChallengPuzzle', 2500, 'Join the matching squares together.The game has several types of blocks, each of which has a connection line, and blocks with the same connection line can be connected. The game is space-themed, the screen is very beautiful, come and experience it.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Escape From Snakes', 2501, 'Escape From Snakes is a fast-paced arcade survival game where danger slithers from every direction! Dodge an endless wave of snakes and try to survive as long as possible. Simple to play but hard to master &amp;mdash; perfect for both casual and competitive players. Can you outlast the swarm?', 'Keyboard or touch or mouse', 'English'),
('Bouncing Balls', 2502, 'If you are finding the champion of time killer, dont miss this Html 5 game Bouncing Balls. It feels like a very simple brick breaker game, but more addictive! It is a simple and minimal game to play because there is no need to pick them up. Just use your finger to tap to aim and shoot the ball and bounce and destroy those bricks. Collect gold circles to get additional balls and get the endless ball chain! Your task is to crush as many bricks as possible before they fall to the ground. Come on! Enjoy the new brand game Bouncing Balls.', 'Swipe your finger to throw the balls and break the bricks Every brick has numbers hit the bricks as many times as the numbers on it to disappear that brick Try to break as many bricks as possible before they move down to the bottom', 'English'),
('Real Cargo Truck Driver 2025', 2503, 'Real Cargo Truck Driver 2025 is an immersive truck simulation game where players transport heavy cargo across challenging roads. Experience realistic driving physics, dynamic weather, and detailed environments as you manage deliveries, upgrade your trucks, and explore expansive open-world routes. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.bestcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.bestcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'WASD to drive', 'English'),
('Labubu and Friends   2Player', 2504, 'Labubu and his friend need to escape the island during summer! Be very careful as you adventure together and collect all the golden clams along the way. Of course, collect those golden clams first &amp;mdash; then reach the giant gift box! Both adorable Labubu friends must make it to the gift box, because inside are their favorite things. But watch out &amp;mdash; the path is full of dangers and obstacles!', 'Use WASD and Arrow keys to move Collect all the Golden Clams and reach the Gift Box Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Thung Thung Sahur Burning Desire', 2505, 'In the chilling silence of a snowy island, a new terror rises &amp;mdash; Tung Tung Sahur, a cursed wooden figure, now possessed by a fiery rage. Once a mere local legend, he&amp;rsquo;s back, swinging his heavy club and ready to burn everything in his path! You play as a brave Minecraft-style Chicken Jockey zombie, armed with nothing but a torch and riding your loyal chicken steed. Your mission? Stop Tung Tung Sahur before his burning desire turns the frozen world to ashes. Key Features: Fight the Wooden Menace &amp;ndash; Face off against a relentless wooden enemy that hates fire&amp;hellip; but hates you more. Ride into Battle &amp;ndash; Mount your chicken and dodge', 'WASD to move Space grab', 'English');
